:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">看看那儿,</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">对</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">家里新添置</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的</span>“</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">家用电器</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">”跃跃欲试,她</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">迫不及待地</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">让</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">师傅帮她</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">手机</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">连上</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\">WIFI</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">。作为一个旁观者</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">,我</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">心中涌上</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">了一阵酸楚</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">??</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">链接</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">WIFI<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">,这个在我们这些年轻人眼里看来再简单不过的动作,竟然让一位</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年过半百的失独</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">老阿姨露出了满足的笑容,她像一个</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">孩子一样,用</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.