\">,记我这个电话,遇到嘛事儿您都叫我,一个电话我就过来,找不到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">我也可以拨打公司的客服</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">95079</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">,</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">24<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">小时</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span>”</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-family:Simsun;font-size:medium;margin-top:15.6pt;margin-bottom:15.6pt;text-indent:21pt;line-height:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">阿姨满怀欣喜地</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">跟我们说:</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">“以前,家里没有安装宽带,</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">一</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">方面</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">是因为经济</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">原因舍</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">不得</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">,另一方面</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">,</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">觉得自己年纪大了,遇到上网等各种问题也不知道该去找谁求助,总怕把手机</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">啊电视啊弄坏</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">,索性不装了,省得麻烦别人。这回好了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">,一</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">根</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">长城宽带,帮我解决了生活</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">中</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的大问题!</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">”阿姨的顾虑我能感受到,想想平常时,父母向我求助一个简单的电脑问题,我都有不耐烦的时候,更能想象到失去独子</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的老</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">阿姨询问无门的景况。看着长城</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">宽带</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">师傅</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">教阿姨上网的画面</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">:一个</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">认真地讲解</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">着</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">,一个认真地学习</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">着</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">,</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">阿姨</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">拿着大麦盒子遥控器小心翼翼地按动换台,</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">很快</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">就</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">学会了如何</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">找到喜欢的电视节目,</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">脸上的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">笑容</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">天真</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">极了</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-family:Simsun;font-size:medium;margin-top:15.6pt;margin-bottom:15.6pt;text-indent:21pt;line-height:24px;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">从这一天起</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">,我也加入</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">了天津长城</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">宽带长爱</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">公益的行动中去,</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">帮助</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">更多的失独老人联络办理爱心宽带。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">就是这样</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">一根</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">看似</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">平常的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">宽带</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">,</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">就</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">能打开</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">老人心灵</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的一扇窗</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">让</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">他们</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">接触外面的世界,了解新鲜</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">的</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">事物,</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">让</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">互联网缤纷内容与</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">他们的生活</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">相伴,也</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">会</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">有</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">更多</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">如我们这样的志愿者与</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">他们</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">沟通</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">让孤单</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">寂寞远离</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">,让快乐解开心结,让</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">健康长寿相随</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">这个社会需要爱,也</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">感谢</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">有责任感、</