mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">爱国歌曲有很多，除了让人在感官上享受愉悦身心，更是能让人汲取精神力量，感化和教育。《中国的版图是火炬》就是这样一首歌。近日，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">该</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">歌曲也将在全网上线，让我们拭目以待。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>','','','2016-08-23 09:59:08','2016-08-24 15:27:38','2','0','0');
