-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">一是</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">锁屏类，通过装上软件，每次点亮手机的时候会先展示广告，需要左右滑屏后再进入，这种应用由于手机分辨率高，要想视觉效果好吸引人就要展示高清广告图，就会非常费流量。并且，滑屏不是每次都有钱，大概开机</span>15<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">左右，有一次赚</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">0.03</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">~0.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元不等的机会。相当于看</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">张广告奖励</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">分钱。记者体验了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">分钟左右，开机</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">次，看了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">150</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">张广告，其中大部分是重复的，最终赚到了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">0.28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元。</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20160830115727_49248.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-