y:宋体;\">万斤口粮，既</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元。为了满足提现要求，记者按照提示邀请了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">个好友，每个好友奖励</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">斤口粮合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">0.03</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元钱，全部累加后竟然还不到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">0.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元。记者计算了下。按照这个速度，除去赠送部分，至少邀请</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">1333</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">人（</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">1333</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">人）才能满足提现要求，一个专业系也没这么多人。简直是不可能完成的任务。</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">后来又体验了其推荐的签到任务，每天签到给</span>500<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">斤口粮（合计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">0.05</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元），也就说大概</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">天能赚到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">毛钱。</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;m