ri;\">23.4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元，这样就已经满足了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">20</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元的提现门槛。整个过程耗时</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">分钟左右。记者带着疑虑进行微信提现，结果是非常顺利地成功从微信提现</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在查看了自己的微信钱包余额增加了</span>20<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元后，记者确认了这次提现的完成。</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">经过上述几家对比来看，赚翻啦（</span>zf.ibczy.com<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">）获得奖励最多，完成时间最短，并且微信提现也非常便捷可靠，同时赚翻啦也同其他应用一样提供了师徒这个收徒体系，因为平台本身的任务奖励非常高，所以就赚翻啦上的‘信而富’这种的任务来说，邀请一个朋友完成就赚</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元，朋友也赚到了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元，记者尝试邀请了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;