;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　　体验一款游戏，翻看十张广告，到商场拍指定产品的条码，拍摄</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">分钟的堵车视频……这些任务看起来都很容易操作，利用一些零碎时间就能完成。任务完成并经过审核，就能得到相应的报酬，并可以通过支付宝、充值话费等方式到账。据了解，有人通过此类</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">可以在一个月内赚到上千元</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">　　那么，这些应用究竟是什么样的呢？用户能赚到多少钱呢？用应用赚钱是否存在隐患呢？带着这些问题，记者也体验了里面一些相关应用。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">　　</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">体验一：</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">惠锁屏</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">　　</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">体验二：钱猪猪</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">体验三：赚翻啦</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><b>&nbsp;</b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">在手机应用市场，记者搜索发现了不少赚钱应用。但总的来看，用户通过这类应用赚钱的方式无非</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">3</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">类。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">一是</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">锁屏类，通过装上软件，每次点亮手机的时候会先展示广告，需要左右滑屏后再进入，这种应用由于手机分辨率高，要想视觉效果好吸引人就要展示高清广告图，就会非常费流量。并且，滑屏不是每次都有钱，大概开机</span>15<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">左右，有一次赚</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">0.03</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">~0.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元不等的机会。相当于看</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">张广告奖励</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">分钱。记者体验了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">分钟左右，开机</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">次，看了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">150</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">张广告，其中大部分是重复的，最终赚到了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">0.28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元。</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20160830115727_49248.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;color:#666666;\">-<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#666666;\">手机致富路，可以走的通么</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#666666;\">-</span></span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12px;color:#666666;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">二是积分兑换类，钱猪猪是今年新上线的应用，属于分享文章类，是一种积分玩法，</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万斤口粮</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">=1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元。</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">上来先送</span>100<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万斤口粮，但提现门槛却高达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万斤口粮，既</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元。为了满足提现要求，记者按照提示邀请了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">个好友，每个好友奖励</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">斤口粮合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">0.03</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元钱，全部累加后竟然还不到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">0.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元。记者计算了下。按照这个速度，除去赠送部分，至少邀请</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">1333</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">人（</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">1333</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">人）才能满足提现要求，一个专业系也没这么多人。简直是不可能完成的任务。</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">后来又体验了其推荐的签到任务，每天签到给</span>500<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">斤口粮（合计</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">0.05</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元），也就说大概</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">天能赚到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">毛钱。</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:C