INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('138','mingtao16','','188','2016083071416','大学校园流行手机赚钱，\'赚翻啦\'最方便','今日头条（ithello）','','15','<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"text-align:center;line-height:1.5;font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">随着生活成本上升，大学生个人消费逐年看涨。</span>“像我们这个学校位置，周边什么都贵，一星期<span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">200</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元根本不够用，现在不敢做校园信贷了，只能不断找稳定赚点的事做做，用时间换空间吧，手机赚钱最近在</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">我们学校特</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">流行，宿舍都互相推荐有个安卓应用</span>‘赚翻啦’上可以做任务赚钱</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">我上个月装的一直做</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">，这月我</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">就</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">增收了</span>200<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元”上海某大学传媒专业大二学生刘嘉佳说。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\"><?xml:namespace prefix = o /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">找一份临工，赚点外快贴补家用，成了不少人喜欢做的事。如今，下载一些手机应用，通过手机完成一些任务也能赚钱。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" src=\"../../upload/20160830115701_90411.png\" /><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　　体验一款游戏，翻看十张广告，到商场拍指定产品的条码，拍摄</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">分钟的堵车视频……这些任务看起来都很容易操作，利用一些零碎时间就能完成。任务完成并经过审核，就能得到相应的报酬，并可以通过支付宝、充值话费等方式到账。据了解，有人通过此类</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">可以在一个月内赚到上千元</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">　　那么，这些应用究竟是什么样的呢？用户能赚到多少钱呢？用应用赚钱是否存在隐患呢？带着这些问题，记者也体验了里面一些相关应用。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">　　</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">体验一：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">惠锁屏</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">　　</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">体验二：钱猪猪</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">体验三：赚翻啦</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">在手机应用市场，记者搜索发现了不少赚钱应用。但总的来看，用户通过这类应用赚钱的方式无非</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">类。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">一是</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">锁屏类，通过装上软件，每次点亮手机的时候会先展示广告，需要左右滑屏后再进入，这种应用由于手机分辨率高，要想视觉效果好吸引人就要展示高清广告图，就会非常费流量。并且，滑屏不是每次都有钱，大概开机</span>15<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">左右，有一次赚</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">0.03</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">~0.2</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元不等的机会。相当于看</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">15</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">张广告奖励</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">分钱。记者体验了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">30</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">分钟左右，开机</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">10</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">次，看了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">150</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">张广告，其中大部分是重复的，最终赚到了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">0.28</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:21pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" src=\"../../upload/20160830115727_49248.png\" /><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:21pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#666666;font-size:12px;\">-<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#666666;font-size:12px;\">手机致富路，可以走的通么</span></span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\"><span style=\"color:#666666;font-size:12px;\">-</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">二是积分兑换类，钱猪猪是今年新上线的应用，属于分享文章类，是一种积分玩法，</span>10<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万斤口粮</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">=1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21pt;\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:10.5pt;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">上来先送</span>100<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万斤口粮，但提现门槛却高达</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万斤口粮，既</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">50</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元。为了满足提现要求，记者按照提示邀请了</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">个好友，每个好友奖励</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">300</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">斤口粮合</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">0.03</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元钱，全部累加后竟然还不到</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">0.1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">元。记者计算了下。按照这个速度，除去赠送部分，至少邀请</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">1333</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">人（</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">1333</span><span style=\"font-famil