INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('144','aidilong','','463','2016090324422','一双袜子治好了儿子的抑郁症','今日头条（天空之城）','','15','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">儿子今年</span>18<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">岁，高三了，是个帅气的大男孩。最爱打篮球，看着球场上挥汗如雨奋力奔跑热情四射的阳光男孩，真是暖到心窝里了。可是最近儿子变得郁郁寡欢，不爱说话了，回家就关进自己的房间，今天竟然告诉我：不想考大学了。我都快急死了，问他怎么了也不说。没办法只好偷偷的给儿子的好朋友打电话，可他们也说不清具体怎么回事，只是说最近经常谈论上大学的事，说上大学了就要住校，几个人一个寝室共同生活。哦??我明白了，知子莫若母，儿子阳光帅气，但有个毛病，从小脚就很臭。以前我也想过不少办法，用药物鞋垫啊偏方泡脚啊之类的，虽然暂时不臭了，但是对脚的伤害也很大，一层层的脱皮、开裂，心疼死我了。可就算这样也维持不了多长时间。儿子很要面子，怕同学嘲笑他，有同学朋友邀请他去家里玩，他从来都不去，就怕脱鞋。慢慢的，儿子的朋友圈越来越小，性格也变得内向，越来越不爱说话，现在甚至连大学也不想考了，再这样下去非得得抑郁症不可。我的心啊，都快着火了，天天上网上手机查怎样治脚臭。有个朋友告诉我，她的朋友圈里有人卖艾蒂龙</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">复合抗菌</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">防臭袜，说效果很好，让我试试。我就是有病乱投医，只要听到治臭脚的，我都要试试，万一有好使的呢，再说一双袜子也没有副作用，穿不坏脚。我立刻让朋友帮我买了一盒。早上让儿子穿上的时候，没告诉他是防臭袜，只说是换双新袜子，怕不好使让他失望。晚上儿子放学回家竟然一边脱鞋一边笑着跟我说：</span>“妈，这双袜子质量挺好的，感觉很吸汗又透气，不像以前跑一天回家脚湿湿的很难受。再给我卖几双吧。”我心里开始兴奋又期待了，说实话，我本来没抱什么希望，毕竟只是双袜子。儿子脱完鞋，我让他把袜子也脱下来我摸摸，果然很干爽</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">而且确实味道比之前的袜子相比小了许多</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">。现在我是真的对这个艾蒂龙防臭袜上了心。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">我就开始上搜索相关信息</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">据了解</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">这是</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">这个复合抗菌防臭袜的纤维里</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">含有铝、锌、铜、银、钛、镁、钙</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">、</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">负离子</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">等天然无机矿物质有效抗菌元素，通过载（置换）的工艺及完善的粒径控制，有效的防止金属离子脱离，保证其安全、稳定、长久的抗菌性能</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">看到这，让</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">我越来越有信心了。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">我用醋把儿子鞋的里面彻底的刷了一遍，目的是除菌。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">一盒六双袜子，我刚开始让儿子每天穿一双新的，儿子自己感觉的特别明显，臭味慢慢的变小了，穿了一周左右吧，只要不贴着脚闻，真的没什么味道了。现在儿子穿着防臭袜，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">四五</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">天不洗也没味道了。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">儿子的同学都说他变了，又自信又爱笑！最主要是正向着心中的大学，奋力前进！我也有目标了，我要做微商，代理艾蒂龙</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">的</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">防臭袜。自己家人穿</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">成本低，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">还能赚钱，我要让所有深受脚臭困扰的人们都穿上艾蒂龙</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">复合抗菌</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">防臭袜。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>','','','2016-09-03 03:49:39','','0','0','1');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('145','aidilong','','194','2016090365000','一双袜子治好了儿子的抑郁症','第一头条','','20','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">儿子今年</span>18<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">岁，高三了，是个帅气的大男孩。最爱打篮球，看着球场上挥汗如雨奋力奔跑热情四射的阳光男孩，真是暖到心窝里了。可是最近儿子变得郁郁寡欢，不爱说话了，回家就关进自己的房间，今天竟然告诉我：不想考大学了。我都快急死了，问他怎么了也不说。没办法只好偷偷的给儿子的好朋友打电话，可他们也说不清具体怎么回事，只是说最近经常谈论上大学的事，说上大学了就要住校，几个人一个寝室共同生活。哦??我明白了，知子莫若母，儿子阳光帅气，但有个毛病，从小脚就很臭。以前我也想过不少办法，用药物鞋垫啊偏方泡脚啊之类的，虽然暂时不臭了，但是对脚的伤害也很大，一层层的脱皮、开裂，心疼死我了。可就算这样也维持不了多长时间。儿子很要面子，怕同学嘲笑他，有同学朋友邀请他去家里玩，他从来都不去，就怕脱鞋。慢慢的，儿子的朋友圈越来越小，性格也变得内向，越来越不爱说话，现在甚至连大学也不想考了，再这样下去非得得抑郁症不可。我的心啊，都快着火了，天天上网上手机查怎样治脚臭。有个朋友告诉我，她的朋友圈里有人卖艾蒂龙</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">复合抗菌</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">防臭袜，说效果很好，让我试试。我就是有病乱投医，只要听到治臭脚的，我都要试试，万一有好使的呢，再说一双袜子也没有副作用，穿不坏脚。我立刻让朋友帮我买了一盒。早上让儿子穿上的时候，没告诉他是防臭袜，只说是换双新袜子，怕不好使让他失望。晚上儿子放学回家竟然一边脱鞋一边笑着跟我说：</span>“妈，这双袜子质量挺好的，感觉很吸汗又透气，不像以前跑一天回家脚湿湿的很难受。再给我卖几双吧。”我心里开始兴奋又期待了，说实话，我本来没抱什么希望，毕竟只是双袜子。儿子脱完鞋，我让他把袜子也脱下来我摸摸，果然很干爽</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">而且确实味道比之前的袜子相比小了许多</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">。现在我是真的对这个艾蒂龙防臭袜上了心。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">我就开始上搜索相关信息</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">据了解</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">这是</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">这个复合抗菌防臭袜的纤维里</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">含有铝、锌、铜、银、钛、镁、钙</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">、</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">负离子</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">等天然无机矿物质有效抗菌元素，通过载（置换）的工艺及完善的粒径控制，有效的防止金属离子脱离，保证其安全、稳定、长久的抗菌性能</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">看到这，让</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">我越来越有信心了。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">我用醋把儿子鞋的里面彻底的刷了一遍，目的是除菌。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">一盒六双袜子，我刚开始让儿子每天穿一双新的，儿子自己感觉的特别明显，臭味慢慢的变小了，穿了一周左右吧，只要不贴着脚闻，真的没什么味道了。现在儿子穿着防臭袜，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">四五</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">天不洗也没味道了。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">儿子的同学都说他变了，又自信又爱笑！最主要是正向着心中的大学，奋力前进！我也有目标了，我要做微商，代理艾蒂龙</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">的</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">防臭袜。自己家人穿</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">成本低，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">还能赚钱，我要让所有深受脚臭困扰的人们都穿上艾蒂龙</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">复合抗菌</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">防臭袜。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';