so-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">而且确实味道比之前的袜子相比小了许多</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">。现在我是真的对这个艾蒂龙防臭袜上了心。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">我就开始上搜索相关信息</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">据了解</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">这是</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">这个复合抗菌防臭袜的纤维里</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">含有铝、锌、铜、银、钛、镁、钙</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">、</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">负离子</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">等天然无机矿物质有效抗菌元素，通过载（置换）的工艺及完善的粒径控制，有效的防止金属离子脱离，保证其安全、稳定、长久的抗菌性能</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">看到这，让</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">我越来越有信心了。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">我用醋把儿子鞋的里面彻底的刷了一遍，目的是除菌。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">一盒六双袜子，我刚开始让儿子每天穿一双新的，儿子自己感觉的特别明显，臭味慢慢的变小了，穿了一周左右吧，只要不贴着脚闻，真的没什么味道了。现在儿子穿着防臭袜，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">四五</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">天不洗也没味道了。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">儿子的同学都说他变了，又自信又爱笑！最主要是正向着心中的大学，奋力前进！我也有目标了，我要做微商，代理艾蒂龙</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">的</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">防臭袜。自己家人穿</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">成本低，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">还能赚钱，我要让所有深受脚臭困扰的人们都穿上艾蒂龙</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">复合抗菌</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">防臭袜。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>','','','2016-09-03 03:52:26','','0','0','1');
