INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('160','aidilong','','192','2016090578799','一双袜子治好了儿子的抑郁症','宁波都市网','http://cn.zxgzw.com/gd/20160905/5727.html','10','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">儿子今年</span>18<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">岁，高三了，是个帅气的大男孩。最爱打篮球，看着球场上挥汗如雨奋力奔跑热情四射的阳光男孩，真是暖到心窝里了。可是最近儿子变得郁郁寡欢，不爱说话了，回家就关进自己的房间，今天竟然告诉我：不想考大学了。我都快急死了，问他怎么了也不说。没办法只好偷偷的给儿子的好朋友打电话，可他们也说不清具体怎么回事，只是说最近经常谈论上大学的事，说上大学了就要住校，几个人一个寝室共同生活。哦??我明白了，知子莫若母，儿子阳光帅气，但有个毛病，从小脚就很臭。以前我也想过不少办法，用药物鞋垫啊偏方泡脚啊之类的，虽然暂时不臭了，但是对脚的伤害也很大，一层层的脱皮、开裂，心疼死我了。可就算这样也维持不了多长时间。儿子很要面子，怕同学嘲笑他，有同学朋友邀请他去家里玩，他从来都不去，就怕脱鞋。慢慢的，儿子的朋友圈越来越小，性格也变得内向，越来越不爱说话，现在甚至连大学也不想考了，再这样下去非得得抑郁症不可。我的心啊，都快着火了，天天上网上手机查怎样治脚臭。有个朋友告诉我，她的朋友圈里有人卖艾蒂龙</span></span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">复合抗菌</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">防臭袜，说效果很好，让我试试。我就是有病乱投医，只要听到治臭脚的，我都要试试，万一有好使的呢，再说一双袜子也没有副作用，穿不坏脚。我立刻让朋友帮我买了一盒。早上让儿子穿上的时候，没告诉他是防臭袜，只说是换双新袜子，怕不好使让他失望。晚上儿子放学回家竟然一边脱鞋一边笑着跟我说：</span>“妈，这双袜子质量挺好的，感觉很吸汗又透气，不像以前跑一天回家脚湿湿的很难受。再给我卖几双吧。”我心里开始兴奋又期待了，说实话，我本来没抱什么希望，毕竟只是双袜子。儿子脱完鞋，我让他把袜子也脱下来我摸摸，果然很干爽</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">而且确实味道比之前的袜子相比小了许多</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">。现在我是真的对这个艾蒂龙防臭袜上了心。</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">我就开始上搜索相关信息</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">据了解</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">这是</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">这个复合抗菌防臭袜的纤维里</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">含有铝、锌、铜、银、钛、镁、钙</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">、</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">负离子</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">等天然无机矿物质有效抗菌元素，通过载（置换）的工艺及完善的粒径控制，有效的防止金属离子脱离，保证其安全、稳定、长久的抗菌性能</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">。</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">看到这，让</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">我越来越有信心了。</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">我用醋把儿子鞋的里面彻底的刷了一遍，目的是除菌。</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">一盒六双袜子，我刚开始让儿子每天穿一双新的，儿子自己感觉的特别明显，臭味慢慢的变小了，穿了一周左右吧，只要不贴着脚闻，真的没什么味道了。现在儿子穿着防臭袜，</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">四五</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">天不洗也没味道了。</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:Calibri;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\"><?xml:namespace prefix = \"o\" /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">儿子的同学都说他变了，又自信又爱笑！最主要是正向着心中的大学，奋力前进！我也有目标了，我要做微商，代理艾蒂龙</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">的</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">防臭袜。自己家人穿</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">成本低，</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">还能赚钱，我要让所有深受脚臭困扰的人们都穿上艾蒂龙</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">复合抗菌</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">防臭袜。</span><span style=\"font-size:14pt;font-family:Calibri;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>','','','2016-09-05 12:20:07','2016-09-05 12:25:33','2','1','0');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('161','客户端发稿','','186','2016091156711','人众金服“众银宝”即将上线   从范冰冰、林心如等女神处学理财逻辑 ','腾讯快报','http://kuaibao.qq.com/s/20160911A0417200','15','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><?xml:namespace prefix = \"o\" /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\">女神之所以成为女神，不仅是长得漂亮，更重要的是活得漂亮。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">范冰冰是如何在一年的时间里赚得</span>1.3亿人民币的？她的吸金大法又有哪些？从柔柔弱弱的紫薇格格摇身一变成为工作室老板，林心如有着怎样的投资理财理念？这些投资理财秘诀又跟我们有着怎样千丝万缕的联系？</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" src=\"../../upload/20160911161027_92284.png\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;text-indent:21pt;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">细数范冰冰的财富之路，在演艺生涯之外，成立公司、入股上市公司、广告代言</span>……范冰冰都玩得顺风顺水。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">对于电影的投资，范冰冰有着自己独到的见解。她在接受媒体采访时曾说道：我敢确保每一部电视剧都可以稳赚。像我的第二部电视剧《金大班》刚有剧本要拍时，所有电视台都来找我预购，包括香港亚视，但我不卖。预购是这样，这部戏能卖到</span>80万一集，现在卖了就是80万，但如果真的做得好，所有电视台都追着买，可能会卖到120万。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">女神的理财逻辑与我们是一样的。</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">一件理财产品如果真的做得好，所有投资人都会追着买！！人众金服精心准备的理财产品</span>“众银宝”即将上线了，你准备好了吗？</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\">据人众金服女神董事长李敏介绍，众银宝系列产品是人众金服在提供供应链金融服务过程中产生的一款面向持票企业的票据质押融资理财产品。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">什么是银行承兑汇票？银行承兑汇票是由银行开具的到期兑付的书面凭证。根据《票据法》第七十三条规定：银行承兑汇票由银行承兑，银行承诺到期后会无条件兑付该票据金额给予该银承的所有人。在众银宝中，银行承兑汇票作为还款保证，项目到期后，若借款人无法按期清偿本息，则该银行承兑汇票由出票银行到期无条件承兑，兑付款项偿还至出借人。安全、灵活、高收益是</span>“众银宝”的关键词。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\">购买了这样的理财产品，</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\">有一天，当有人</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\">问及你对于豪门的态度时，你也可以像范冰冰这样讲出一句：</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\">我不嫁豪门，我自己就是豪门！</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\">自己是豪门的除了金锁，还有紫薇格格。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">在</span>2015年的福布斯中国名人榜上，出道于1994年的林心如，除了2009年和2010年未进入榜单以外，每年均榜上有名。去年综合排名第82位，收入为1780万元。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\">2009年，林心如离开前经纪公司华谊兄弟后，选择自立门户，成立了林心如工作室。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\">根据当时媒体的报道，成立之初的工作室规模并不大，只有经纪、助理和宣传三个部门，每个部门也只有两名员工。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">两年后，林心如转型担任电视剧制作人，并开始投资影视剧。对于林心如工作室的收入情况，并没有过多的公开性报道。不过，根据腾讯娱乐</span>2013年的一篇报道，林心如曾在接受媒体采访时，她并不否认自己身价过亿：</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">品尝了身价过亿的果实之后，林心如曾开心地说：</span>“当老板真不错，我要继续投资拍戏，以后要躺着赚钱。” 据统计，截至2014年，林心如工作室已参与制作7部影视作品。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">在理财方面，林心如自称</span>“真正开始存钱是2001年之后，当时做的第一件事情是给家人买房子。”此外，她把所有的收入都交给了父母，让他们帮自己理财，自己也购买了一些理财产品。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">那么林心如是否会购买我们的</span></span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\">众银宝？答案显而易见。</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">这款安全、灵活、稳健的理财产品将于</span>9月14日上线，相信林心如也会动心的！</span><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;line-height:150%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:150%;\">&nbsp;</p>','','','2016-09-11 04:14:19','2016-09-11 16:22:28','2','1','0');
