t:0px;margin-top:14px;line-height:25px;padding-right:0px;background-color:#f7fbff;\">　　据众银宝所属平台人众金服董事长李敏介绍，众银宝是人众金服面向广大投资者推出的一款以银行承兑汇票为质押担保，安全、灵活、稳健的理财产品。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0px;font-size:14px;font-family:宋体, Arial, sans-serif;padding-bottom:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-left:0px;margin-top:14px;line-height:25px;padding-right:0px;background-color:#f7fbff;\">　　据悉，“众银宝”借款人均为企业法人，借款企业只能出具银行承兑汇票作为质押担保依据，确保投资者资金的安全。投资者投资后，最快第一个工作日内即可实现稳健收益。提现时，资金最快一个工作日内即可到达投资者指定账户。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0px;font-size:14px;font-family:宋体, Arial, sans-serif;padding-bottom:0px;padding-top:0px;padding-left:0px;margin-top:14px;line-height:25px;padding-right:0px;background-color:#f7fbff;\">　　董事长李敏还讲到，众银宝收益高、安全、灵活、便捷，正是以后发展的大趋势，因为它存在的目的就是为投资人提供一个更加安全、稳妥、便捷的理财方式，这与互联网金融“普惠金融”的定位不谋而合。</p>','','','2016-09-24 09:15:32','2016-09-26 12:32:03','3','1','0');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('175','客户端发稿','','184','2016092853736','一上线就被抢，还要不断加推！！人众金服的“众惠宝”怎么了？','腾讯客户端','http://view.inews.qq.com/a/20160928A07G4J00','9','<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;“行业可以</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">不同</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">途径可以不同，速度也可以不同</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">但是各行各业中，产业与资本的</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">渗透</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">与</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">融合</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">却是相通的</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">。供应链金融</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">便是产业链资源</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">与金融资本跨界的融合。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">正是</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">跨界融合孕育</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">了</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">全新的商业逻辑和投资机会</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">。</span>”是日，在回答投资人为何人众金服选择专注供应链金融领域的提问时，人众金服董事长李敏从行业发展趋势进行了解读。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><?xml:namespace prefix = \"o\" /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">李敏还谈到，</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">供应链金融作为产业模式升级的自然演化</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">具有深厚的行业根基，颠覆了传统金融</span>“基于金融而金融”的范式，兼具金融的爆发力和产业的持久性。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">无独有偶，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">中国人民大学商学院副院长宋华</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">也曾提出</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，供应链金融一定要先有资产，没有一个好的产业逻辑和业务逻辑就不要去谈金融。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">对于自</span>2013年成立以来就专注供应链金融的人众金服来说，在供应链金融框架下，寻求优质资产端正成为金融业务的关键要素之一。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" src=\"../../upload/20160928182431_30157.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"800\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">因为，资产端有关行业空间大小、行业格局及核心企业对上下游中小企业的把控力，只有知己知彼才能百战百胜，掌握了理财产品的核心关键</span>??风控，投资者才能选出真正好标的。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">而这，也正是人众金服全新升级理财产品</span>“众惠宝”一经上线，便被抢购一空，而今仍在不断加推的深层次原因。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">之所以受到投资人此般青睐，人众金服董事长李敏认为，这是因为</span>“众惠宝”所依托的核心企业??中商惠民实力与影响力皆备。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">“平台在选择核心企业时除了应重点关注企业的信用状况是否良好、经营规模是否够大、行业地位是否具有影响力与说服力等因素，一般以行业龙头企业作为核心企业的主要选择，这样可防止所选行业的系统性风险和企业的道德风险等问题。”李敏谈到。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">据悉，中商惠民以社区</span>O2O运营服务为核心，于2012年9月正式上线运营，致力于为居民社区，商业社区和大学社区提供生活商品配送。9月5日，中商惠民获得新一轮13亿人民币B轮融资，目前估值已过百亿。同时，经过与众多竞标公司共同经历严格的层层筛选与综合考察，凭借完善的线上线下渠道，强大的仓储物流体系，中商惠民正式成为军队采购网2016-2017年度供货商，用事实证明实力。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;“</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">能够</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">与这样</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">优质</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">的</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">资产</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">端合作，我们</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">就像是抓住了行业发展的命脉，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">正是如此，我们可以</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">在风险控制的关键环节形成自己的竞争优势。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">”李敏告诉在场的许多投资人。“</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">至于核心企业的中下游企业的融资需求方面，平台可根据由核心企业提出的推荐函，以及中下游相关企业销售与账目等详细数据，进行严格审核与考察，为投资人资金安全保驾护航。</span>”</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">　</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">　</span>“作为</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">专注供应链金融的</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">平台，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">人众金服具有绝佳风控能力的</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">基因决定了</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">我们</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">拥有</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">比</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">其他企业获得</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">更多</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">优质资产</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">端</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">的能力。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">而</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">我们可以利用自身的优势寻求更多的优质资产</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，开发出更优质的大众理财产品</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">。</span>”</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">李敏董事长还</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">表示</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，正是这样的良性循环</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">使平台得以在供应链金融资产端方面保持独有的竞争优势。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>','','','2016-09-28 06:26:06','','2','1','0');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('176','客户端发稿','','195','2016092853736','一上线就被抢，还要不断加推！！人众金服的“众惠宝”怎么了？','凤凰客户端','','5','<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;“行业可以</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">不同</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">途径可以不同，速度也可以不同</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">但是各行各业中，产业与资本的</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">渗透</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">与</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">融合</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">却是相通的</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">。供应链金融</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">便是产业链资源</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">与金融资本跨界的融合。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">正是</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">跨界融合孕育</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">了</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">全新的商业逻辑和投资机会</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">。</span>”是日，在回答投资人为何人众金服选择专注供应链金融领域的提问时，人众金服董事长李敏从行业发展趋势进行了解读。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><?xml:namespace prefix = \"o\" /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">李敏还谈到，</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">供应链金融作为产业模式升级的自然演化</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">具有深厚的行业根基，颠覆了传统金融</span>“基于金融而金融”的范式，兼具金融的爆发力和产业的持久性。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">无独有偶，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">中国人民大学商学院副院长宋华</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">也曾提出</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，供应链金融一定要先有资产，没有一个好的产业逻辑和业务逻辑就不要去谈金融。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">对于自</span>2013年成立以来就专注供应链金融的人众金服来说，在供应链金融框架下，寻求优质资产端正成为金融业务的关键要素之一。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" src=\"../../upload/20160928182431_30157.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"800\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">因为，资产端有关行业空间大小、行业格局及核心企业对上下游中小企业的把控力，只有知己知彼才能百战百胜，掌握了理财产品的核心关键</span>??风控，投资者才能选出真正好标的。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">而这，也正是人众金服全新升级理财产品</span>“众惠宝”一经上线，便被抢购一空，而今仍在不断加推的深层次原因。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">之所以受到投资人此般青睐，人众金服董事长李敏认为，这是因为</span>“众惠宝”所依托的核心企业??中商惠民实力与影响力皆备。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">“平台在选择核心企业时除了应重点关注企业的信用状况是否良好、经营规模是否够大、行业地位是否具有影响力与说服力等因素，一般以行业龙头企业作为核心企业的主要选择，这样可防止所选行业的系统性风险和企业的道德风险等问题。”李敏谈到。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">据悉，中商惠民以社区</span>O2O运营服务为核心，于2012年9月正式上线运营，致力于为居民社区，商业社区和大学社区提供生活商品配送。9月5日，中商惠民获得新一轮13亿人民币B轮融资，目前估值已过百亿。同时，经过与众多竞标公司共同经历严格的层层筛选与综合考察，凭借完善的线上线下渠道，强大的仓储物流体系，中商惠民正式成为军队采购网2016-2017年度供货商，用事实证明实力。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;“</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">能够</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">与这样</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">优质</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">的</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">资产</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">端合作，我们</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">就像是抓住了行业发展的命脉，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">正是如此，我们可以</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">在风险控制的关键环节形成自己的竞争优势。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">”李敏告诉在场的许多投资人。“</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">至于核心企业的中下游企业的融资需求方面，平台可根据由核心企业提出的推荐函，以及中下游相关企业销售与账目等详细数据，进行严格审核与考察，为投资人资金安全保驾护航。</span>”</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">　</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">　</span>“作为</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">专注供应链金融的</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">平台，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">人众金服具有绝佳风控能力的</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">基因决定了</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">我们</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">拥有</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">比</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">其他企业获得</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">更多</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">优质资产</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">端</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">的能力。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">而</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">我们可以利用自身的优势寻求更多的优质资产</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，开发出更优质的大众理财产品</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">。</span>”</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">李敏董事长还</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">表示</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，正是这样的良性循环</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">使平台得以在供应链金融资产端方面保持独有的竞争优势。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>','广告','','2016-09-28 06:26:06','','3','1','0');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('180','客户端发稿','','184','2016101375750','驻藏某团新建家属楼完工','腾讯客户端','','9','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">（杜德胜报道）近日，驻西藏某团新建家属楼装修完毕，即将交付使用，新建的家属楼将有效解决官兵探亲家属来队住房难问题。这是该团大抓基础设施建设，为基层官兵办的实事之一。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">我军士官制度改革以来，随着该团士官比例逐年增长，原来的营房不能满足需求。官兵家属临时来队找房愈加困难，许多官兵来队后只能住招待所或临时腾出的集体宿舍。该团党委把解决官兵家属临时来队住房难作为为兵服务的一件大事，认真听取基层意见，筹措专项资金兴建探亲家属楼。兴建家属楼的动态得到官兵广泛关注，团党委坚持</span>“公开招标、透明施工、跟踪验收”的标准严密施工，确保官兵能按时圆满的住上“放心楼”。年底交房后，官兵家属临时来队探亲将可直接入住。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"../../upload/20161013164727_63574.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">此次共兴建来队探亲住房</span>200<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">余套，每套面积四五十平方米，设有卧室、客厅、厨房、卫生间，床、椅、电视、热水器等生活设施一应俱全，来队探亲家属生活条件将大大改善。</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>','','','2016-10-13 04:47:47','','0','0','1');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('177','客户端发稿','','293','2016092853736','一上线就被抢，还要不断加推！！人众金服的“众惠宝”怎么了？','搜狐媒体','','5','<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;“行业可以</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">不同</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">途径可以不同，速度也可以不同</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">但是各行各业中，产业与资本的</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">渗透</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">与</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">融合</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">却是相通的</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">。供应链金融</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">便是产业链资源</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">与金融资本跨界的融合。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">正是</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">跨界融合孕育</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">了</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">全新的商业逻辑和投资机会</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">。</span>”是日，在回答投资人为何人众金服选择专注供应链金融领域的提问时，人众金服董事长李敏从行业发展趋势进行了解读。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">李敏还谈到，</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">供应链金融作为产业模式升级的自然演化</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">具有深厚的行业根基，颠覆了传统金融</span>“基于金融而金融”的范式，兼具金融的爆发力和产业的持久性。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">无独有偶，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">中国人民大学商学院副院长宋华</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">也曾提出</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，供应链金融一定要先有资产，没有一个好的产业逻辑和业务逻辑就不要去谈金融。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">对于自</span>2013年成立以来就专注供应链金融的人众金服来说，在供应链金融框架下，寻求优质资产端正成为金融业务的关键要素之一。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20160928182431_30157.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"800\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">因为，资产端有关行业空间大小、行业格局及核心企业对上下游中小企业的把控力，只有知己知彼才能百战百胜，掌握了理财产品的核心关键</span>??风控，投资者才能选出真正好标的。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">而这，也正是人众金服全新升级理财产品</span>“众惠宝”一经上线，便被抢购一空，而今仍在不断加推的深层次原因。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">之所以受到投资人此般青睐，人众金服董事长李敏认为，这是因为</span>“众惠宝”所依托的核心企业??中商惠民实力与影响力皆备。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">“平台在选择核心企业时除了应重点关注企业的信用状况是否良好、经营规模是否够大、行业地位是否具有影响力与说服力等因素，一般以行业龙头企业作为核心企业的主要选择，这样可防止所选行业的系统性风险和企业的道德风险等问题。”李敏谈到。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">据悉，中商惠民以社区</span>O2O运营服务为核心，于2012年9月正式上线运营，致力于为居民社区，商业社区和大学社区提供生活商品配送。9月5日，中商惠民获得新一轮13亿人民币B轮融资，目前估值已过百亿。同时，经过与众多竞标公司共同经历严格的层层筛选与综合考察，凭借完善的线上线下渠道，强大的仓储物流体系，中商惠民正式成为军队采购网2016-2017年度供货商，用事实证明实力。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;“</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">能够</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">与这样</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">优质</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">的</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">资产</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">端合作，我们</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">就像是抓住了行业发展的命脉，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">正是如此，我们可以</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">在风险控制的关键环节形成自己的竞争优势。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">”李敏告诉在场的许多投资人。“</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">至于核心企业的中下游企业的融资需求方面，平台可根据由核心企业提出的推荐函，以及中下游相关企业销售与账目等详细数据，进行严格审核与考察，为投资人资金安全保驾护航。</span>”</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">　</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">　</span>“作为</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">专注供应链金融的</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">平台，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">人众金服具有绝佳风控能力的</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">基因决定了</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">我们</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">拥有</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">比</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">其他企业获得</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">更多</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">优质资产</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">端</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">的能力。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">而</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">我们可以利用自身的优势寻求更多的优质资产</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，开发出更优质的大众理财产品</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">。</span>”</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">李敏董事长还</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">表示</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，正是这样的良性循环</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">使平台得以在供应链金融资产端方面保持独有的竞争优势。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>','广告','','2016-09-28 06:26:06','','3','1','0');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('178','客户端发稿','','458','2016092853736','一上线就被抢，还要不断加推！！人众金服的“众惠宝”怎么了？','网易客户端（优吃客）','http://c.m.163.com/news/a/C22SOA9Q05228LNH.html','5','<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;“行业可以</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">不同</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">途径可以不同，速度也可以不同</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">但是各行各业中，产业与资本的</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">渗透</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">与</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">融合</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">却是相通的</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">。供应链金融</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">便是产业链资源</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">与金融资本跨界的融合。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">正是</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">跨界融合孕育</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">了</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">全新的商业逻辑和投资机会</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">。</span>”是日，在回答投资人为何人众金服选择专注供应链金融领域的提问时，人众金服董事长李敏从行业发展趋势进行了解读。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><?xml:namespace prefix = \"o\" /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">李敏还谈到，</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">供应链金融作为产业模式升级的自然演化</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">具有深厚的行业根基，颠覆了传统金融</span>“基于金融而金融”的范式，兼具金融的爆发力和产业的持久性。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">无独有偶，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">中国人民大学商学院副院长宋华</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">也曾提出</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，供应链金融一定要先有资产，没有一个好的产业逻辑和业务逻辑就不要去谈金融。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">对于自</span>2013年成立以来就专注供应链金融的人众金服来说，在供应链金融框架下，寻求优质资产端正成为金融业务的关键要素之一。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" src=\"../../upload/20160928182431_30157.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"800\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">因为，资产端有关行业空间大小、行业格局及核心企业对上下游中小企业的把控力，只有知己知彼才能百战百胜，掌握了理财产品的核心关键</span>??风控，投资者才能选出真正好标的。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">而这，也正是人众金服全新升级理财产品</span>“众惠宝”一经上线，便被抢购一空，而今仍在不断加推的深层次原因。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">之所以受到投资人此般青睐，人众金服董事长李敏认为，这是因为</span>“众惠宝”所依托的核心企业??中商惠民实力与影响力皆备。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">“平台在选择核心企业时除了应重点关注企业的信用状况是否良好、经营规模是否够大、行业地位是否具有影响力与说服力等因素，一般以行业龙头企业作为核心企业的主要选择，这样可防止所选行业的系统性风险和企业的道德风险等问题。”李敏谈到。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">据悉，中商惠民以社区</span>O2O运营服务为核心，于2012年9月正式上线运营，致力于为居民社区，商业社区和大学社区提供生活商品配送。9月5日，中商惠民获得新一轮13亿人民币B轮融资，目前估值已过百亿。同时，经过与众多竞标公司共同经历严格的层层筛选与综合考察，凭借完善的线上线下渠道，强大的仓储物流体系，中商惠民正式成为军队采购网2016-2017年度供货商，用事实证明实力。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;“</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">能够</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">与这样</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">优质</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">的</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">资产</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">端合作，我们</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">就像是抓住了行业发展的命脉，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">正是如此，我们可以</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">在风险控制的关键环节形成自己的竞争优势。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">”李敏告诉在场的许多投资人。“</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">至于核心企业的中下游企业的融资需求方面，平台可根据由核心企业提出的推荐函，以及中下游相关企业销售与账目等详细数据，进行严格审核与考察，为投资人资金安全保驾护航。</span>”</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">　</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">　</span>“作为</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">专注供应链金融的</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">平台，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">人众金服具有绝佳风控能力的</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">基因决定了</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">我们</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">拥有</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">比</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">其他企业获得</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">更多</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">优质资产</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">端</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">的能力。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">而</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">我们可以利用自身的优势寻求更多的优质资产</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，开发出更优质的大众理财产品</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">。</span>”</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">李敏董事长还</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">表示</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，正是这样的良性循环</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">使平台得以在供应链金融资产端方面保持独有的竞争优势。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>','','','2016-09-28 06:26:06','','2','1','0');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('179','客户端发稿','','500','2016092853736','一上线就被抢，还要不断加推！！人众金服的“众惠宝”怎么了？','今日头条随机','','5','<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;“行业可以</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">不同</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">途径可以不同，速度也可以不同</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">但是各行各业中，产业与资本的</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">渗透</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">与</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">融合</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">却是相通的</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">。供应链金融</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">便是产业链资源</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">与金融资本跨界的融合。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">正是</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">跨界融合孕育</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">了</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">全新的商业逻辑和投资机会</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">。</span>”是日，在回答投资人为何人众金服选择专注供应链金融领域的提问时，人众金服董事长李敏从行业发展趋势进行了解读。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><?xml:namespace prefix = \"o\" /><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">李敏还谈到，</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">供应链金融作为产业模式升级的自然演化</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">具有深厚的行业根基，颠覆了传统金融</span>“基于金融而金融”的范式，兼具金融的爆发力和产业的持久性。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">无独有偶，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">中国人民大学商学院副院长宋华</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">也曾提出</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，供应链金融一定要先有资产，没有一个好的产业逻辑和业务逻辑就不要去谈金融。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">对于自</span>2013年成立以来就专注供应链金融的人众金服来说，在供应链金融框架下，寻求优质资产端正成为金融业务的关键要素之一。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" src=\"../../upload/20160928182431_30157.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"800\" />&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">因为，资产端有关行业空间大小、行业格局及核心企业对上下游中小企业的把控力，只有知己知彼才能百战百胜，掌握了理财产品的核心关键</span>??风控，投资者才能选出真正好标的。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">而这，也正是人众金服全新升级理财产品</span>“众惠宝”一经上线，便被抢购一空，而今仍在不断加推的深层次原因。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">之所以受到投资人此般青睐，人众金服董事长李敏认为，这是因为</span>“众惠宝”所依托的核心企业??中商惠民实力与影响力皆备。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">“平台在选择核心企业时除了应重点关注企业的信用状况是否良好、经营规模是否够大、行业地位是否具有影响力与说服力等因素，一般以行业龙头企业作为核心企业的主要选择，这样可防止所选行业的系统性风险和企业的道德风险等问题。”李敏谈到。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">据悉，中商惠民以社区</span>O2O运营服务为核心，于2012年9月正式上线运营，致力于为居民社区，商业社区和大学社区提供生活商品配送。9月5日，中商惠民获得新一轮13亿人民币B轮融资，目前估值已过百亿。同时，经过与众多竞标公司共同经历严格的层层筛选与综合考察，凭借完善的线上线下渠道，强大的仓储物流体系，中商惠民正式成为军队采购网2016-2017年度供货商，用事实证明实力。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;“</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">能够</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">与这样</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">优质</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">的</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">资产</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">端合作，我们</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">就像是抓住了行业发展的命脉，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">正是如此，我们可以</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">在风险控制的关键环节形成自己的竞争优势。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">”李敏告诉在场的许多投资人。“</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">至于核心企业的中下游企业的融资需求方面，平台可根据由核心企业提出的推荐函，以及中下游相关企业销售与账目等详细数据，进行严格审核与考察，为投资人资金安全保驾护航。</span>”</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">　</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">　</span>“作为</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">专注供应链金融的</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">平台，</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">人众金服具有绝佳风控能力的</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">基因决定了</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">我们</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">拥有</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">比</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">其他企业获得</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">更多</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">优质资产</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">端</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">的能力。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">而</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">我们可以利用自身的优势寻求更多的优质资产</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，开发出更优质的大众理财产品</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;\">。</span>”</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">李敏董事长还</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">表示</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，正是这样的良性循环</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">使平台得以在供应链金融资产端方面保持独有的竞争优势。</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:仿宋_GB2312;mso-spacerun:\'yes\';mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>','拒','','2016-09-28 06:26:06','2016-09-28 19:20:36','3','1','0');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('181','客户端发稿','','516','2016101375750','驻藏某团新建家属楼完工','今日头条','','5','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">（杜德胜报道）近日，驻西藏某团新建家属楼装修完毕，即将交付使用，新建的家属楼将有效解决官兵探亲家属来队住房难问题。这是该团大抓基础设施建设，为基层官兵办的实事之一。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">我军士官制度改革以来，随着该团士官比例逐年增长，原来的营房不能满足需求。官兵家属临时来队找房愈加困难，许多官兵来队后只能住招待所或临时腾出的集体宿舍。该团党委把解决官兵家属临时来队住房难作为为兵服务的一件大事，认真听取基层意见，筹措专项资金兴建探亲家属楼。兴建家属楼的动态得到官兵广泛关注，团党委坚持</span>“公开招标、透明施工、跟踪验收”的标准严密施工，确保官兵能按时圆满的住上“放心楼”。年底交房后，官兵家属临时来队探亲将可直接入住。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"../../upload/20161013164727_63574.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">此次共兴建来队探亲住房</span>200<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">余套，每套面积四五十平方米，设有卧室、客厅、厨房、卫生间，床、椅、电视、热水器等生活设施一应俱全，来队探亲家属生活条件将大大改善。</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>','','','2016-10-13 04:47:47','','0','0','1');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('182','18092567723','','518','2016101424581','王博:用诗歌纪念长征胜利80周年（图）','凤凰客户端','','15','<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:10px 0px 0px;font-family:微软雅黑;color:#333333;font-size:14px;line-height:25px;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.seekforchina.com/uploads/allimg/161014/1-1610140ZK3960.jpg\" original=\"/uploads/allimg/161014/1-1610140ZK3960.jpg\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border:none;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:26px 0px 0px;color:#333333;font-size:14px;border:0px;word-wrap:break-word;line-height:26px;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　<span style=\"border:0px;margin:0px;padding:0px;\">长征精神是中华民族百折不挠、自强不息民族精神的最高表现，是保证我们革命和建设事业从弱小走向强大的精神力量。长征，在人类历史上前所未有、极其伟大，它所创造的英雄业绩无与伦比，它是中国革命史上的奇迹，也是世界军事史上的伟大壮举，我们后人将永远铭记这段辉煌史篇，传承中华民族优秀革命传统、践行伟大长征精神，挥舞强军力量走向新时代的万里长征。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:26px 0px 0px;font-family:??????, ????;color:#333333;font-size:14px;border:0px;word-wrap:break-word;line-height:26px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;\">　　</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', Tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;text-indent:2em;background-color:#fafafc;\">　</span><strong style=\"font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', Tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;text-indent:2em;\">七律?长征</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:12px 0px;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', Tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;background-color:#fafafc;\">　　（一）</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:12px 0px;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', Tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;background-color:#fafafc;\">　　雄关铁索??路，</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:12px 0px;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', Tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;background-color:#fafafc;\">　　拔斩沟峰岳谷开。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:12px 0px;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', Tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;background-color:#fafafc;\">　　赤水翻腾风剑滚，</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:12px 0px;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', Tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;background-color:#fafafc;\">　　黔江咆哮血舟拍。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:12px 0px;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', Tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;background-color:#fafafc;\">　　泸关浪堑挟颅破，</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:12px 0px;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', Tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;background-color:#fafafc;\">　　渡口涛雷?骨裁。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:12px 0px;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', Tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;background-color:#fafafc;\">　　万壑云崖非鬼府，</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:12px 0px;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', Tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;background-color:#fafafc;\">　　壮心不死凯旋来。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:12px 0px;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', Tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;background-color:#fafafc;\">　　（二）</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:12px 0px;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', Tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;background-color:#fafafc;\">　　披甲横戈二万五，</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:12px 0px;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', Tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;background-color:#fafafc;\">　　逼逢血刃剑光寒。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:12px 0px;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', Tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;background-color:#fafafc;\">　　草泽踏卷苍鹰落，</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:12px 0px;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', Tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;background-color:#fafafc;\">　　雪岭奔飞铁马残。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:12px 0px;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', Tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;background-color:#fafafc;\">　　破斩千钧凭树骨，</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:12px 0px;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', Tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;background-color:#fafafc;\">　　驰行万里倚冰川。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:12px 0px;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', Tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;background-color:#fafafc;\">　　胸前浪火成灰烬，</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:12px 0px;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', Tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;background-color:#fafafc;\">　　蹄下云雷碾作烟。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:12px 0px;text-indent:2em;color:#333333;font-family:\'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', Tahoma, arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;background-color:#fafafc;\">　　（作者：王博，吉林省公主岭人，青年诗词作家）</p>','','','2016-10-14 10:39:03','','0','0','1');
