INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('198','a351910080','','517','2016112981490','“丁丁”危机  小偏方效果胜韭菜多倍！','新浪看点','http://k.sina.cn/article_5926120321_161396b810010018lk.html','8','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:150%;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#ff0000;font-size:15pt;\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30pt;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">两性生活中，和谐的性生活对于构建和睦家庭至关重要，奈何现代都市男性压力急剧增加，不少男性三十五岁之后就出现未老先衰症状，经常腰酸腰疼，肾气不足，虽说对于房事兴趣还在，但是多少有些力不从心。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30pt;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">面对妻子的小渴望，摆脱丁丁危机势在必行。补肾虽不是大事，但是盲目地乱吃药对于身体的伤害也是特别巨大的。科学食疗方式是当今时代最被推崇的补肾方式。今天主要来推荐几道操作起来相对容易又补肾养气的食疗菜谱。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:150%;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;font-size:12pt;\">一、中药泡茶</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">原料：须花参</span>1-2克、枸杞10粒、红茶2-3克。 </span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">做法：将三种原料开水闷泡</span>5分钟左右，即可食用，每天只放一次作料可反复冲泡，直到水无色无味。 </span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:24pt;line-height:150%;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161129190134_52956.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">功效：连服</span>10天为一个食疗周期，连服10天后，停服5天。一般坚持使用一个月，肾虚阳痿疲软不举腰膝酸软现象可得到显著改善，性欲望强烈，时间延长，性生活质量大大提升，房事可获得充分满足感。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">优点：操作简单、天然无副作用，持续服用从根本上提高肾功能，温肾壮阳、大补元气。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">温馨提醒：为达到更好效果，建议使用特级须花参，正品须花参带有</span>“防伪验证码”。须花参每天不可超3克。此茶不宜与萝卜、藜芦同食。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:12pt;text-indent:23.15pt;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:12pt;\">二、红烧鳝鱼</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161129190149_12419.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">黄鳝是非常好的补虚补血的食材，尤其是对病后体虚，身体虚弱，营养不良有较好的滋补营养作用。而且味道鲜美，让补肾变成了一种享受。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:150%;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:12pt;\">三、腰果虾仁</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:24pt;line-height:150%;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161129190210_25001.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">虾仁是典型的高蛋白、低脂肪食物，易于吸收，具有补肾壮阳、健胃的功效，腰果营养十分丰富，香美可口，并有一定的食疗作用，它可润肠通便，润肤美容，延缓衰老，补肾之功效。经常食用可以提高机体抗病能力。腰果虾仁不仅色香味俱全，而且补肾效果俱佳。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;line-height:150%;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:12pt;\">四、韭菜枸杞伴核桃</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:24pt;line-height:150%;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161129190245_95668.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30pt;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">此道菜就是专为补肾人士打造，核桃仁能补肾固精，与同样补肾的佳品韭菜强强联手，再加上枸杞的助力，成为最经典的补肾气的药膳佳肴。尤其适宜易疲劳乏力的上班族食用。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30pt;line-height:150%;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:12pt;\">五、黄花熘猪腰</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:30pt;line-height:150%;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161129190304_23194.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30pt;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">黄花熘猪腰是一道补肾又补血的营养健康菜。非常适合肾阳虚症型骨质增生症患者食用。猪腰是最能补肾养血的一种食品。具有补肾气、通膀胱、消积滞、止消渴之功效。可用于治疗肾虚腰痛、水肿、耳聋等症。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30pt;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">另外除了在饮食上营养搭配外，还应该注意加强体育锻炼，同时改掉一些吸烟酗酒的不良嗜好，保持良好的生活习惯，重新唤醒丁丁的战斗力就看你的坚持了！</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>','','','2016-11-29 07:04:29','','2','1','0');
