indent:24pt;text-align:center;line-height:22.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161129191216_26303.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-indent:24pt;line-height:22.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">肾虚患者可以多进行散步、慢跑、瑜珈、打网球、打太极等运动方式，要坚持进行，持之以恒，增强自身抵抗力。推荐一组简单的踮脚运动补肾养气。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:11.2500pt;margin-bottom:11.2500pt;line-height:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　</span> (1)两足平行，足距同肩宽，目视正前方，两臂自然下垂，两掌贴于裤缝，手指自然张开。足跟提起，连续呼吸9次。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:11.2500pt;margin-bottom:11.2500pt;line-height:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　　</span>(2)足跟落地，吸气，慢慢曲膝下蹲，两手背逐渐转前，虎口对脚踝;手接近地面时，稍用力抓成拳(有抓物之意)，吸足气。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:11.2500pt;margin-bottom:11.2500pt;line-height:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　　</span>(3)憋气，身体逐渐起立，两手下垂，逐渐握紧拳头。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:11.2500pt;margin-bottom:11.2500pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;line-height:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">(4)呼气，身体立正，两臂外拧，拳心向前，两肘从两侧挤压软肋，同时身体和脚跟部用力上提，并提肛，呼吸。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:11.2500pt;margin-bottom:11.2500pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;line-height:21.0000pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">饮食补肾</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-top:11.2500pt;margin-bottom:11.2500pt;text-indent:24.0000pt;text-align:center;line-height:21.0000pt;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161129191229_43511.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;line-height:22.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在日常饮食中也有不少食材对于补肾的功效很显著的。虾味道鲜美，补益和药用作用都较高。淡菜又名珠菜、壳菜，含丰富蛋白质、碘、</span>B族维生素、锌、铁、钙、磷等。其味咸，性温，有温肾固精、益气补虚功效。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-indent:24pt;line-height:22.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">泥鳅虽然其貌不扬，但含优质蛋白质、脂肪、维生素</span> A、维生素 B1、烟酸、铁、磷、钙等。其味甘，性平，有补中益气、养肾生精功效。对调节性功能有较好的作用。泥鳅中含一种特殊蛋白质，有促进</span><a href=\"http://nan.99.com.cn/bjxts/238746.htm\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">精子</span></a><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">形成作用。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:11.25pt;text-indent:24pt;line-height:22.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">补肾的方法其实有很多，注意要根据自己的实际情况选择适合自己的方式。两性关系的维护需要正常的夫妻性生活，挽救两性危机，补肾行动势在必行。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>','','','2016-11-29 07:12:53','','2','1','0');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('200','a351910080','','520','2016113095921','经常“亮红灯”？四招让你变回“老司机”！','简书','http://www.jianshu.com/p/0d1edd9751bd','5','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;line-height:24px;text-indent:24pt;\">冬天将要来临，天气寒冷是最容易损耗肾之阳气的，肾虚的人在冬季容易风寒、腰酸腿软、嗜睡，应尽快补肾，以保证冬天不会加重症状。中医认为，食疗法和按摩法，既无副作用，又能见效果，对男人补肾是非常合适的。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;line-height:24px;text-indent:24pt;\"><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161130112219_21307.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\">中药之王：补肾</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\">茶</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">原料：须花参</span>1-2克、枸杞10粒、红茶2-3克。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">做法：将三种原料开水闷泡</span>5分钟左右，即可食用，每天只放一次作料可反复冲泡，直到水无色无味。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:24pt;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161130112248_88162.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">功效：连服</span>10天为一个食疗周期，连服10天后，停服5天。一般坚持使用一个月，肾虚阳痿疲软不举腰膝酸软现象可得到显著改善，性欲望强烈，时间延长，房事可获得充分满足。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\">优点：操作简单、天然无副作用，持续服用从根本上提高肾功能，温肾壮阳、大补元气。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">温馨提醒：为达到更好效果，建议使用特级须花参，正品须花参带有</span>“防伪验证码”。须花参每天不可超过3克。此茶不宜与萝卜、藜芦一同食用。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\">海中之王：海参进补</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:24pt;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161130112304_67027.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;海参性味咸、温，有补肾壮阳、益气滋阴、通肠润燥等作用，堪称补肾壮阳之佳品，对男子肾虚引起的羸弱消瘦、小便频数、腰膝酸软、性机能减退有奇效，经常食用海参，能起到较好的食疗效果。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\">老少皆宜：搓耳朵补肾</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:24pt;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161130112554_90661.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\">用两手掌心紧按两耳外耳道，两手的食指、中指和无名指分别轻轻敲击脑后枕骨。然后掌心掩按外耳道，手指紧按脑后枕骨不动，再很快抬离，这时耳中有放炮样声响。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">中医认为，肾开窍于耳，这三个动作反复做上</span>5-10次，每日做2-3次，会有耳聪目明、调剂补元、强本固肾的作用，无论是在起床后还是睡前，只要你有时间，都可以做一下这些动作，绝对是“物美价廉”、老少皆宜的补肾良方。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\">人体第二心脏：泡脚补肾</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:24pt;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161130112619_27273.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">双脚是人体的</span>“第二心脏”，上面的涌泉穴、三阴交都能够刺激肾脏。因此，每天晚上用热水泡脚，不仅能促进血液循环，还有补肾的作用。而且泡脚能够减轻疲劳，帮助好眠，是一举多得的补肾方法。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\">这些补肾方法，无论是来一杯暖暖的</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\">中药</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:24px;font-size:12pt;\">茶，还是在夜晚享受一回温热的泡脚，将能够帮助肾虚的人补肾固元，不惧寒气，重拾健康活力。</span></p>','','','2016-11-30 11:27:30','','2','1','0');
