INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('203','a351910080','','520','2016113014089','这一招 男人用了“持续久”老司机最爱！','简书','http://www.jianshu.com/p/08318c711bb6','5','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-indent:30.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;text-align:center;line-height:150%;\"><b style=\"line-height:150%;text-indent:30pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:15pt;\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">肾是生命之源，从古到今人类对于补肾养肾的研究从未曾间断过。</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">现代都市，由于男性肩上所承载的多重压力更是导致不少男性年纪轻轻就出现腰酸腰疼肾气不足。近八成成年男性呈现出对夫妻房事有心无力的状况。</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">而夫妻性生活和谐在两性生活中占据非常巨大的比重，久而久之很容易导致两性矛盾不断升级，进而直接影响家庭和谐，婚姻稳固。补肾也就变成了挽救婚姻必不可少的一项行动了。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:24pt;line-height:150%;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161130160151_39061.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">然而有不少人为了追求一时的快感，选择用极速特效药来提高肾脏活力，这不仅是起不到补肾的目的，还因为药物中含有大量激素而直接造成对身体其它器官的损伤，长期服用很有可能导致肾功能完全罢工。实际上补肾可以按照科学的方式进行，食疗搭配运动来补肾，补肾效果看得见，而且对身体没有任何伤害，确实是不错的补肾方式。先来看看从古沿用至今的一些补肾好方法。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;line-height:150%;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:12pt;\">中药泡茶</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">原料：须花参</span>1-2克、枸杞10粒、红茶2-3克。 </span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">做法：将三种原料开水闷泡</span>5分钟左右，即可食用，每天只放一次作料可反复冲泡，直到水无色无味。 </span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:24pt;line-height:150%;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161130160206_43338.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">功效：连服</span>10天为一个食疗周期，连服10天后，停服5天。一般坚持使用一个月，肾虚阳痿疲软不举腰膝酸软现象可得到显著改善，性欲望强烈，时间延长，性生活质量大大提升，房事可获得充分满足感。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">优点：操作简单、天然无副作用，持续服用从根本上提高肾功能，温肾壮阳、大补元气。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">温馨提醒：为达到更好效果，建议使用特级须花参，正品须花参带有</span>“防伪验证码”。须花参每天不可超3克。此茶不宜与萝卜、藜芦同食。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:24pt;line-height:150%;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161130160222_41187.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">补肾除了须花参茶饮外，还可以搭配一些补肾的食材。比如韭菜作为蔬菜界的伟哥，多吃韭菜可以益气补肾。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">补肾蔬菜之王黄秋葵肉质柔嫩多汁，口感润滑，具有特殊的香气和风味</span>;适合火锅、爆炒、凉拌、煎炸、羹汤等多种烹调方法。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">黑色食物入肾，因此日常生活中多吃黑豆、黑米、黑枣、黑芝麻、黑木耳等补肾功效都是很不错的。鱼虾海鲜也可以适当地补充，有助于补肾气，同时补充肾脏所缺的多重营养。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:24pt;line-height:150%;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161130160236_64118.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">除了饮食上注意保养外，日常生活中还可以搭配适量的运动。慢跑、打太极都是非常强肾健体的运动，日常生活中可以多做。通过适量的体育锻炼可以起到促进血液循环加速肾脏排毒的目的。久而久之对于肾脏机能的恢复大有裨益。另外像一些球类运动比如打网球打羽毛球等都是运动强度不算大，非常适合肾虚人群进行的运动。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24pt;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">补肾并非难事，重要的是要按照科学</span> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的方式进补，不可为了追求快速见效而去乱选择药物，要知道是药三分毒。想要在床上有炉火纯青的表现，补肾养气是必不可少的。</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';line-height:150%;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>','','','2016-11-30 04:02:59','','2','1','0');
