INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('224','千里','','515','2016120759229','太子乐奶粉怎么样 太子乐奶粉质量如何？','天天快报','','5','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">2016年</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">国家食药监</span>“月月检”的例行通报中</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">，</span>88家婴幼儿配方乳粉企业222批次样品</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">全部合格，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">哈尔滨太子乳品工业有限公司名列其中。太子乐提供安全、营养、健康的奶粉，对奶粉品质严格管控，实现了对妈妈们的承诺。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">太子乐以专业的态度、严谨的作风生产适合中国宝宝体质的好奶粉，精明的消费者会选择适合自己的奶粉，太子乐以卓越品质成就行业标杆，以科技为依托，做有社会责任感的企业，成为国内知名品牌。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\">太子乐奶粉怎么样？优秀品质始于源头</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">　　为了保持生乳新鲜，太子乐直接将生乳通过管线进入制冷罐及时冷却，且规定所有生乳须在</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">24小时内加工完。太子乐奶粉首选的奶源供应地位于北纬46度的呼兰大草原，素有“江省邹鲁”、“满洲谷仓”的美誉，是世界闻名的牧场。太子乐从奶源到生产、销售的全过程对环境卫生要求相当高。太子乐工厂远离了城市市中心区和重工业区，避免了</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">各种污染，环境非常干净，其优越的环境，肥沃的土壤，丰富的草原，优良的草质，为太子乐奶粉提供了高品质的新鲜牛奶资源，确保从源头上保证太子乐奶粉的产品品质。太子乐制定了高于国家的内控标准，对原料、半成品和成品进行层层检测，凡是不合格的原料一律禁止入厂，不合格的产品绝不许出厂，从奶源到生产，从检验到入库，太子公司以整个产业链为基础，做到每罐奶粉都安全可靠。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\">太子乐奶粉怎么样？工艺做保障</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">太子乐奶粉采用干湿复合工艺，通过压力喷雾干燥和气力密相干混方式，保证基粉和营养素均匀混合并不破坏奶粉的颗粒，使冲调口感更好。同时采用微胶囊包埋技术避免复合维生素、核苷酸、</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">AA、DHA等营养成分在加工中受到破坏，为宝宝保存最好的营养。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">通过先进的技术充分保证营养元素不被破坏和更好吸收。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\">太子乐奶粉怎么样？监督质检有原则</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐的每一罐产品在生产时都严格按照八</span>“不”原则来把控，这八“不”原则指的就是：超过</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">24小时的生乳不采集；不合格的原辅料不使用；不清楚生产日期的原料不投料；本道工序不合格的产品不许流入下一道工序；不合格的产品不装箱；发现问题的产品不入库；不体检的员工不许上岗；卫生不合格不许生产。每一罐奶粉经过八“不”原则的监督后，为宝宝提供优质健康奶粉。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">太子乐始终保持认真负责的态度，近年来一直狠抓内功，投重资建立世界一流的研发、生产、检验团队，不断升级产品配方，丰富产品线，专心做好奶粉。哈尔滨太子乳品工业有限公司，是首批获全国工业产品婴幼儿配方奶粉生产许可证的企业。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>','','','2016-12-07 05:53:45','','0','0','1');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('225','千里','','520','2016120749322','太子乐奶粉怎么样 新跨越新高度','简书','','5','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐奶粉产品从原料入厂到出厂都要经过严格的质量检验，所有原料进厂批批检验合格后方可使用，产品必须批批检验合格后方可出厂。</span>2016年</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\">，太子乐奶粉应时而变，借势</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\">国产奶粉新政，启动品牌战略升级计划，精简产品结构，打造明星产品系列，致力于重新定义国产奶粉新标准。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">太子乐在不断的发展探索中，持续创新，现如今已形成了一条品质优良、配方科学、安全有保障的产品系列。在太子乐奶粉强大的产品阵容中，金装</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">a乳清蛋白系列、金装金100系列、金装FOS系列、DHA系列等都非常受欢迎。太子乐全力打造适合中国宝宝体质的奶粉，按照中国母乳的“黄金标准”研发而出的高端产品Graclove挚悦、铂金乐怡、铂金100，为宝宝健康快乐成长增添动力。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">新跨越新高度，太子乐奶粉怎么样？借势打造明星产品，更在产品配方、产品质量、全方位服务、社会公益等多个方面全新打造优质品牌。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">太子乐奶粉严格把控，多重检验。太子乐运用国内外一流的食品检验设备和技术手段，对质量安全进行全程控制，使产品更具品质保证。成就婴幼儿奶粉行业中的著名品牌，太子乐奶粉为打造一流的奶粉品牌而不断前进，让妈妈心里更踏实。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">市场的多元化挑战带给奶粉行业更多的惊喜，太子乐应时而变新产品上市打造明星产品，为的是给宝宝提供更有针对性的营养，更贴心的关爱。太子乐奶粉自成立之日起，就用心做好产品的同时，关注家庭环境，愿为家庭和谐幸福添一份力。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">奶粉行业作为关系着国民健康，关系着国家未来的行业，在产品质量安全，生产工艺等各个方面都需要严格把控。太子乐奶粉怎么样？在定期的奶粉行业抽检报告中显示，太子乐奶粉质量达标，抽检各方面指标合格。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>','','','2016-12-07 05:56:51','','0','0','1');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('226','千里','','531','2016120759474','太子乐奶粉怎么样 质量就是生命领跑乳品行业','搜狐媒体','','8','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐以</span>“安全健康，诚信服务”为质量方针，“每天太子乐，健康又快乐!”是太子乐品牌的长期追求。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐作为国产乳品企业领跑者，旗下太子乐挚悦、太子乐铂金乐怡、太子乐铂金</span>100等明星产品深受消费者喜爱与信赖。同时，太子乐乳业不仅关爱儿童成长健康，更关心家庭每一位成员的身体健康，太子乐乳业特推出孕产妇奶粉、女士奶粉，以及安美全家奶粉，为家庭每个成员带去健康放心营养的同时，给宝宝营造一个更和谐美好的环境。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">“质量就是生命，出厂的每一罐奶粉必须安全“这就是太子乐作出的承诺，太子乐都有决心、有信心通过不懈努力，不仅使太子乐在国内的乳制品行业中成为领航者和相关标准的制定者，而且在国际乳制品行业中有更多的参与度和话语权，但是，信心恢复是一个漫长而艰苦的过程，尤其不能让类似的质量问题再度发生，只有彻底从机制上保证对奶粉质量问题“绝不容忍”，并长期坚持下去，国产奶粉今后的路才能越走越宽。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐奶粉作为婴幼儿奶粉行业中的著名品牌，一直为做出好奶粉不懈努力。一个品牌是品牌理念价值、产品服务、市场定位和消费心理的综合表现，同时又是一种策略竞争，一种定位过程的开始。创建品牌为你的品牌蒸蒸日上、日日生机打下坚实的基础。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">品牌形象是当前国产奶粉企业面临的重要问题，在这方面太子乐奶粉走在了前列。太子乐奶粉是国内较早进入奶粉行业并专注奶粉生产的企业，一直专注科研实力，拥有自己的研发团队，严格进行产品检验，配方不断升级，这些都是太子乐树立良好品牌形象的重要表现，为太子乐树立良好的品牌形象奠定基础。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;\">太子乐奶粉怎么样？一路走来，通过自身的不断努力，凭借不断提高的产品质量，逐渐获得了国家行业协会和消费者的一致肯定，在奋力前行的路上不断的收获着鲜花与掌声。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>','','','2016-12-07 06:01:11','','0','0','1');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('227','千里','','516','2016120738347','太子乐奶粉最新事件：慈善的铺筑者?太子乐步履实而行远','今日头条','','5','<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">从通过新浪育儿专家问诊到微课传播知识，以及期待具备医学问诊知识的机器人的诞生，与婴儿有关的产品已经颠覆</span>21 世纪初我们对母婴世界的设想。2016</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">新浪育儿年度盛典</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">在北京富力万丽酒店盛大开幕</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">，太子乐受邀出席活动并与行业专家</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">粉丝妈妈</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">等共话育儿之道。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161207180558_97061.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">明星大咖助阵展示当代育儿人风采</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">本次盛典特别邀请了来自演艺界的明星妈妈冉莹颖，知名演员黄小蕾，妇产科专家马良坤，自媒体达人丽丽猫儿，移动电商领军人物张良伦做精彩演讲，现场分享她们的育儿故事，现场气氛活跃，嘉宾们有趣的故事博得了阵阵掌声。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">十大育儿新闻</span></b><b><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">公共安全</span></b><b><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">倍受</span></b><b><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">关注</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">2016年母婴盛典十大新闻聚焦儿童安全、公共安全、社会秩序、社会政策和母婴潮流，为广大母婴关注者提供精准的分析</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">2016十大育儿新闻包括《内地小孩地铁哭闹 香港男子大吼怒推婴儿车》等在内的公共安全事件；雾霾、甲醛、二手烟相关的公共环境事件；电话手表隐患；父母监护不到位引发的儿童意外事件；毒跑道事件；二孩放开第二年；母乳喂养；海淘政策；山东疫苗事件以及留学低龄化。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">慈善的铺筑者：太子乐步履实而行远</span></b></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161207181211_84157.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\r\n</span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\">在备受关注的颁奖环节太子乐</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">脱颖而出，荣获</span>2016年度“社会公益践行”品牌</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">。回顾</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">2016年太子乐公益之路步履实而行远：</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">2016年3月，太子乳业联手宝宝树开展了“BabyBox&amp;太子乐专属奶粉礼盒”活动</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">2016年4月，太子乳业为辣妈们提供分享交流的平台，发起“辣妈分享罐”活动</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">2016年7月，太子</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">乳业为武汉洪涝安置点</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">成立爱心捐助组，</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">并捐助价值</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">20万元的奶粉。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">2016年</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">太子乐收获满满，不仅铺筑的公益路不断延伸，产品质量也得到了行业的一致认可：</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">2016年1月10日，太子乐荣获“2015年度质量优秀奖”；2016年8月，太子乐荣获《“太子乐金装?乳清蛋白”荣获2016年度技术进步一等奖》及《优秀新产品奖》</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">2016新浪育儿盛典在一片喝彩声中落幕，但盛典所带来的行业知识</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">育儿经验</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">、</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">未来发展与公益</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">温暖将伴随每一个人：</span>“</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">养育之道，勿忘初心</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">”。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-right:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;padding:0pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\"><br />\r\n</span></b></p>','','','2016-12-07 06:12:34','','0','0','1');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('228','千里','','516','2016120736114','太子乐奶粉最新事件：匠心不变初心未改助力公益前行','今日头条','','5','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">11月24日，</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">数位育儿专家、亲子专家、自媒体人、政府相关人士以及数位明星大咖</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">等</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">共</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">聚</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">新浪育儿年度盛典</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">探讨行业发展。同时对孕婴童行业中的优秀企业进行表彰，哈尔滨太子乳业</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">荣获</span>2016年度“社会公益践行”品牌</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161207181814_16124.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">作为</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">新浪育儿频道举办的第九个育儿年度盛典</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">，本次的盛典主题是</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">“</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">未来</span>+家</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">”。“</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">未来</span>+家</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">”</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">需要每一颗匠心把一切善意执念推送往前，遵循初心，以匠人之念对待未来，期许美好。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161207181836_73080.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐以匠人之心打造</span>“让妈妈放心的好奶粉”</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<h1 style=\"margin:0pt;text-indent:23pt;padding:0pt;vertical-align:baseline;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:normal;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐奶粉品质保障，从奶源到技术到质检，太子乐都做到层层把关，每一个环节都做到细致用心，太子乐</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:normal;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">在奶源上精选北纬</span>46度东北黑土带的奶源</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:normal;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:normal;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">所有生乳采集地都采用先进的榨乳设备，从牛体榨出的生乳直接通过管线进入制冷罐，再由公司的保温车直接拉到厂房，避免了生乳与空气接触的机会，防止生乳受到细菌的污染。所有生乳须在</span>24小时内完成加工，既保证了生乳的新鲜又保证了产品的品质。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:normal;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐秉承</span>“质量就是生命”的经营发展理念，实施全过程标准化生产、全方位智能化检测，产品质量得到了国家、行业协会以及消费者的一致肯定。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-weight:normal;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></h1>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐以善意执念推动社会公益前行</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">2016年3月，太子乐乳业联手宝宝树为贫困地区口粮无保障的孩子们送去安全放心的奶粉</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">；</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">2016年6月，太子乐携手襄阳市保康爱湾婴幼举办了“关爱贫困山区留守儿童”大型公益活动，为</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">保康大安教学点</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">的</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">孩子</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">捐赠学习用品与太子乐礼包；</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">016年7月，太子乐</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">为武汉市洪涝灾区</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">捐赠</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">价值</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">20万</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">元的</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">奶粉，</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">并及时向受灾群众捐献物资</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\">。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:24.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">母婴界的未来</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">家将要通向何方？</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">通过新浪育儿年度</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">盛典</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">更全面准确的把握母婴界的发展变化的脉搏，</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">面对</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">机遇与挑战</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐相关负责人表示：</span>“太子乐将依旧以匠人之心打造‘</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">让妈妈放心的好奶粉</span>’，以善意执念践行社会公益，面对未来太子乐满怀信心</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;letter-spacing:0pt;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: