yle=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">个民主国家的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">92</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">位前政要组成，是全世界上影响力最大的前政要联盟；后者凝聚了世界各地诸多知名商界和业界领袖。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;<img src=\"../../upload/20161219140346_17918.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">维姆?科克透过马德里俱乐部和欧洲各国的卸任国家元首和行政首长合作，共同致力于提升民主素质和全球共同体的改革。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161219140403_81542.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\r\n<!--[endif]--></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">荷兰前首相维姆?科克与棠果旅居</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">金东哲亲切握手会谈</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">金东哲表示热烈欢迎维姆?科克的到访，并向他详细介绍了棠果的业务布局及发展规划，邀请他体验极具中国特色的棠果民宿，并赠与维姆?科克中国书法“分享世界”作为会面礼物，希望他将棠果“共享经济，分享世界”的文化与使命分享到荷兰及欧洲各地。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161219140419_12090.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\r\n<!--[endif]--></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">维姆?科克认为棠果极具发展潜力，在获悉棠果海外市场已全面开展的消息，更表示，欢迎棠果在荷兰开拓市场，荷兰以海堤、风车、郁金香和宽容的社会风气而闻名，是非常美丽的国度，欢迎华人朋友到荷兰旅游观光。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p><img src=\"../../upload/20161219140437_67826.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\r\n</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">棠果致力打造全球一站式旅居平台的棠果旅居，自上线以来，发展迅速，得到了全国乃至全世界的关注，受到奥地利总理维尔纳</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">法伊曼、西班牙前首相何塞?路易斯?萨帕特罗等多个国家前政要密切关注，棠果创始人金东哲表示，会尽快与各个国家旅游住宿领域相关部门开展密切合作，让棠果遍布全球，为华人出游提供便利。</span><a name=\"_GoBack\"></a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161219140452_27311.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\r\n<!--[endif]--></span></p>','','','2016-12-19 02:06:15','','3','1','0');
