me-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">科克中国书法“分享世界”作为会面礼物，希望他将棠果“共享经济，分享世界”的文化与使命分享到荷兰及欧洲各地。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><img src=\"../../upload/20161219140419_12090.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\r\n<!--[endif]--></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">维姆</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times Newroman&quot;;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-bidi;mso-ansi-language:EN-US;mso-fareast-language:ZH-CN;mso-bidi-language:AR-SA;\">?</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">科克认为棠果极具发展潜力，在获悉棠果海外市场已全面开展的消息，更表示，欢迎棠果在荷兰开拓市场，荷兰以海堤、风车、郁金香和宽容的社会风气而闻名，是非常美丽的国度，欢迎华人朋友到荷兰旅游观光。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p><img src=\"../../upload/20161219140437_67826.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\r\n</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-l