ial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:21pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">此太子乐奶粉最新事件时间</span>:2016年11月24日,</span></b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">一年一度的新浪育儿盛典于</span>2016年11月24日在北京富力万丽酒店隆重开幕，本届年度盛典的主题为“未来+家”，这是新浪育儿频道举办的第九个育儿年度盛典，作为有公众影响力的媒体，新浪育儿已成为育儿领域的黄金品牌。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">太子乐奶粉怎么样？</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐乳业在此次新浪育儿盛典上再创辉煌，凭借品牌自身实力及在</span>2016年中所做出的贡献，被评为2016年度“社会公益践行”品牌。</span><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐奶粉最新事件</span>:荣获三项大奖 厚积薄发持续发展</span></b><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:21pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">此太子乐奶粉最新</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">事件时间：</span>2016年8月20日,</span></b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">中国乳制品工业协会年会暨第十六次乳品技术精品展示会上，太子乐作为受邀企业，亮相广州。此次乳协年会及技术展会为期三日，以</span>“携手全球乳业共发展”为主题，以“为行业提供交流学习平台，促进行业健康持续发展”为使命，评选出了业内优秀企业和产品，以此肯定企业的付出和努力。</span><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:21pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐奶粉咋样？哈尔滨太子乳品工业有限公司在中国乳制品工业协会第二十二次年会荣获</span>“优秀新产品奖”、“技术进步一等奖”、“质量管理优秀企业”等三项大奖。中国乳制品工业协会为太子乐颁发奖项，是对太子乐品牌的肯定，更是对太子乐今后继续研发新产品的一种鼓励和支持。太子乐作为一个有良心的民族企业，将带给社会更优质的产品和更多的爱。</span><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐奶粉最新事件</span>:开展“铁打的妈妈 流水的女神”大型公益互动活动</span></b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:等线;line-height:150%;font-size:13.5pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:21pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">此太子乐奶粉最新</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">事件时间：</span>2016年8月6日</span></b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">,为传递社会正能量，践行企业社会责任，共建美好幸福家庭生活。6日，由哈尔滨太子乳品工业有限公司发起的“铁打的妈妈流水的女神”大型互动活动正式启动。太子乐奶粉咋样？活动不仅引发广大市民，特别是众多85后妈妈的广泛关注，一些业内专业人士也纷纷肯定此次活动，并给予大力点赞。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:21pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">85后的一代多是独生子女，这一代女性大多作为父母掌上明珠而长大，婚后被丈夫宠爱，一旦生子，全家的关注点都转移到宝宝身上，新妈妈身体和心理的落差逐渐显现，这急需被重视和改观。太子乐奶粉怎么样？这些准妈妈幸福感如何提升，如何才能更有利于宝宝身心成长，这些都成了当下最受人关心关注的心理热点问题。为此，活动现场太子奶业员工和现场邀请的心理咨询专家和她们进行了零距离互动，心贴心交流，使众多的85后准妈妈们耳提面授获益匪浅。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐奶粉最新事件</span>:十年服务铸就社会最暖色 太子乐荣获两项大奖</span></b><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:21pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">此太子乐奶粉最新事件时间</span>:</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\">&nbsp;2016年7月20-22日</span></b><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">,</span></b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">第</span>16届CBME中国孕婴童展在上海虹桥国家会展中心举行。共2,366家展商，3,673个品牌参展，共同打造孕婴童行业健康发展的产业氛围。7月21日下午15:15分，中国孕婴童产业至高荣誉CBME AWARDS中国孕婴童产业奖在Cool Kids Fashion秀场揭晓。太子乐荣获“服务十年奖”和“服务社会奖两大奖项。”鼓励太子乐从事中国孕婴童产业15年来不断创新进取，为产业发展做出卓越贡献;感谢太子乐大力发展慈善事业,为完善社会救助体系做出贡献。</span><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:21pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐奶粉怎么样？太子乐总经理付大鹤先生出席颁奖典礼接受媒体专访时表示：</span>“太子乐2001年成立，是首批获得全国工业产品婴幼儿奶粉生产资质的企业。太子乐秉承“质量就是生命”的经营发展理念，实施全过程标准化生产、全方位智能化检测，产品质量得到了国家、行业协会以及消费者的一致肯定。”</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐奶粉最新事件</span>:太子乐荣获“2015年度质量优秀奖”，月月抽检全部合格</span></b><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:21pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">此太子乐奶粉最新事件时间：</span>2016年1月10日,</span></b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">2016年1月10日，中国乳制品工业协会在北京召开了“2015年度乳制品质量工作会议”。“2015年度质量优秀奖”获奖名单在会上揭晓。</span><a href=\"http://www.qbaobei.com/shypbk/bbyp/ye/20130309_255907.html\" title=\"国产奶粉\"><u><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#fa4e68;font-size:10.5pt;\">国产奶粉</span></u></a><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">品牌太子乐奶粉获得</span>“质量优秀奖”，再次获得殊荣。</span><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:21pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">太子乐奶粉怎么样？太子乐自成立以来，便致力于婴幼儿</span><a href=\"http://www.qbaobei.com/yebk/xse/rgwy/20130712_269837.html\" title=\"配方奶\"><u><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#fa4e68;font-size:10.5pt;\">配方奶</span></u></a><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">粉的生产与研发，为中国万千家庭送去放心，安全，适合中国宝宝体质的健康好奶粉。在刚刚过去的一年之中，太子乐奶粉在中国乳制品协会组织的对市场主流婴幼儿乳粉</span>“月月抽检”中全部合格。太子乐不断获得行业协会的认可，也正是对其用实际行动争做国产奶粉放心品牌的莫大鼓励。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐奶粉最新事件</span>:太子乐铂金100荣获奶粉新秀奖</span></b><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:21pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">此太子乐奶粉最新事件时间：</span>2016年</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\">12</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">月</span>1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\">2</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">日</span>,</span></b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">宝宝成长过程中所接触的各方面环境对于宝宝一生的发展有着重要的影响。太子乐针对这一现象，升级配方，为宝宝提供一款新产品，成长百分百组合</span>??太子乐铂金</span><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">100。</span><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐奶粉咋样？</span></span><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">2016年12月12日，“2016年第8届母婴用品评测盛典”榜单揭晓：太子乐铂金100幼儿配方奶粉获奶粉新秀奖。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>','','','2016-12-20 09:19:20','','2','1','0');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('257','千里','','517','2016122078469','太子乐奶粉最新事件成焦点 厚积薄发获各方好评','新浪看点','http://k.sina.cn/article_5926120321_161396b8100100195g.html?from=tech&vt=4','8','<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐奶粉最新事件</span>:2016新浪育儿获</span></b><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">”</span></b><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">社会公益实践奖</span></span></b><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">”</span></b><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:21pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">此太子乐奶粉最新事件时间</span>:2016年11月24日,</span></b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">一年一度的新浪育儿盛典于</span>2016年11月24日在北京富力万丽酒店隆重开幕，本届年度盛典的主题为“未来+家”，这是新浪育儿频道举办的第九个育儿年度盛典，作为有公众影响力的媒体，新浪育儿已成为育儿领域的黄金品牌。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">太子乐奶粉怎么样？</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐乳业在此次新浪育儿盛典上再创辉煌，凭借品牌自身实力及在</span>2016年中所做出的贡献，被评为2016年度“社会公益践行”品牌。</span><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐奶粉最新事件</span>:荣获三项大奖 厚积薄发持续发展</span></b><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:21pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">此太子乐奶粉最新</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">事件时间：</span>2016年8月20日,</span></b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">中国乳制品工业协会年会暨第十六次乳品技术精品展示会上，太子乐作为受邀企业，亮相广州。此次乳协年会及技术展会为期三日，以</span>“携手全球乳业共发展”为主题，以“为行业提供交流学习平台，促进行业健康持续发展”为使命，评选出了业内优秀企业和产品，以此肯定企业的付出和努力。</span><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:21pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐奶粉咋样？哈尔滨太子乳品工业有限公司在中国乳制品工业协会第二十二次年会荣获</span>“优秀新产品奖”、“技术进步一等奖”、“质量管理优秀企业”等三项大奖。中国乳制品工业协会为太子乐颁发奖项，是对太子乐品牌的肯定，更是对太子乐今后继续研发新产品的一种鼓励和支持。太子乐作为一个有良心的民族企业，将带给社会更优质的产品和更多的爱。</span><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐奶粉最新事件</span>:开展“铁打的妈妈 流水的女神”大型公益互动活动</span></b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:等线;line-height:150%;font-size:13.5pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:21pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">此太子乐奶粉最新</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">事件时间：</span>2016年8月6日</span></b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">,为传递社会正能量，践行企业社会责任，共建美好幸福家庭生活。6日，由哈尔滨太子乳品工业有限公司发起的“铁打的妈妈流水的女神”大型互动活动正式启动。太子乐奶粉咋样？活动不仅引发广大市民，特别是众多85后妈妈的广泛关注，一些业内专业人士也纷纷肯定此次活动，并给予大力点赞。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:21pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">85后的一代多是独生子女，这一代女性大多作为父母掌上明珠而长大，婚后被丈夫宠爱，一旦生子，全家的关注点都转移到宝宝身上，新妈妈身体和心理的落差逐渐显现，这急需被重视和改观。太子乐奶粉怎么样？这些准妈妈幸福感如何提升，如何才能更有利于宝宝身心成长，这些都成了当下最受人关心关注的心理热点问题。为此，活动现场太子奶业员工和现场邀请的心理咨询专家和她们进行了零距离互动，心贴心交流，使众多的85后准妈妈们耳提面授获益匪浅。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐奶粉最新事件</span>:十年服务铸就社会最暖色 太子乐荣获两项大奖</span></b><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:21pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">此太子乐奶粉最新事件时间</span>:</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\">&nbsp;2016年7月20-22日</span></b><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">,</span></b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">第</span>16届CBME中国孕婴童展在上海虹桥国家会展中心举行。共2,366家展商，3,673个品牌参展，共同打造孕婴童行业健康发展的产业氛围。7月21日下午15:15分，中国孕婴童产业至高荣誉CBME AWARDS中国孕婴童产业奖在Cool Kids Fashion秀场揭晓。太子乐荣获“服务十年奖”和“服务社会奖两大奖项。”鼓励太子乐从事中国孕婴童产业15年来不断创新进取，为产业发展做出卓越贡献;感谢太子乐大力发展慈善事业,为完善社会救助体系做出贡献。</span><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:21pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐奶粉怎么样？太子乐总经理付大鹤先生出席颁奖典礼接受媒体专访时表示：</span>“太子乐2001年成立，是首批获得全国工业产品婴幼儿奶粉生产资质的企业。太子乐秉承“质量就是生命”的经营发展理念，实施全过程标准化生产、全方位智能化检测，产品质量得到了国家、行业协会以及消费者的一致肯定。”</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐奶粉最新事件</span>:太子乐荣获“2015年度质量优秀奖”，月月抽检全部合格</span></b><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:21pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">此太子乐奶粉最新事件时间：</span>2016年1月10日,</span></b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">2016年1月10日，中国乳制品工业协会在北京召开了“2015年度乳制品质量工作会议”。“2015年度质量优秀奖”获奖名单在会上揭晓。</span><a href=\"http://www.qbaobei.com/shypbk/bbyp/ye/20130309_255907.html\" title=\"国产奶粉\"><u><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#fa4e68;font-size:10.5pt;\">国产奶粉</span></u></a><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">品牌太子乐奶粉获得</span>“质量优秀奖”，再次获得殊荣。</span><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:21pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">太子乐奶粉怎么样？太子乐自成立以来，便致力于婴幼儿</span><a href=\"http://www.qbaobei.com/yebk/xse/rgwy/20130712_269837.html\" title=\"配方奶\"><u><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#fa4e68;font-size:10.5pt;\">配方奶</span></u></a><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">粉的生产与研发，为中国万千家庭送去放心，安全，适合中国宝宝体质的健康好奶粉。在刚刚过去的一年之中，太子乐奶粉在中国乳制品协会组织的对市场主流婴幼儿乳粉</span>“月月抽检”中全部合格。太子乐不断获得行业协会的认可，也正是对其用实际行动争做国产奶粉放心品牌的莫大鼓励。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐奶粉最新事件</span>:太子乐铂金100荣获奶粉新秀奖</span></b><b><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"p\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;text-indent:21pt;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">此太子乐奶粉最新事件时间：</span>2016年</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\">12</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">月</span>1</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\">2</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">日</span>,</span></b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">宝宝成长过程中所接触的各方面环境对于宝宝一生的发展有着重要的影响。太子乐针对这一现象，升级配方，为宝宝提供一款新产品，成长百分百组合</span>??太子乐铂金</span><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">100。</span><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐奶粉咋样？</span></span><span class=\"16\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">2016年12月12日，“2016年第8届母婴用品评测盛典”榜单揭晓：太子乐铂金100幼儿配方奶粉获奶粉新秀奖。</span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;line-height:150%;color:#333333;font-size:10.5pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>','','','2016-12-20 09:20:10','','2','1','0');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('258','千里','','513','2016122046930','聚焦奶粉行业新趋势 太子乐奶粉卖点受广泛关注','网易客户端','http://c.m.163.com/news/a/C8NN48L605228LNH.html','8','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">自奶粉新政实施以来，各大乳企纷纷行动，都在为注册事宜做着准备。太子乐奶粉怎么样？</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">太子乐近年来一直狠抓内功，投重资建立世界一流的研发、生产、检验团队，太子乐不断升级产品配方，丰富产品线。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐奶粉应时而变，隆重推出太子乐奶粉挚悦、太子乐奶粉铂金乐怡、太子乐奶粉铂金</span>100等多款明星产品，为了给宝宝更好的爱。太子乐奶粉最新事件：太子乐铂金100荣获PCbaby评测盛典奶粉新秀奖。太子乐奶粉咋样？奶粉特点富含人体生长发育必需的脂肪酸亚油酸、亚麻酸，亚油酸、亚麻酸是组织细胞的重要组织成分，与神经系统和儿童的成长发育有密切关系，人体自身不能合成，必须从食物中摄取。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">太子乐奶粉卖点是什么？</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">太子乐工厂远离了城市市中心区和重工业区，避免了各种污染，环境非常干净，其优越的环境，肥沃的土壤，丰富的草原，优良的草质，为太子乐奶粉提供了高品质的新鲜牛奶资源，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">在这片位于北纬</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">46°的神奇地带，有着世界闻名的牧场、农场种植园，环境和资源得天独厚。其肥沃的土壤，丰富的草原，优良的草质，为奶牛提供了最天然舒适的生存环境，为“太子乐”产品提供了高品质的鲜牛奶资源</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">确保从源头上保证太子乐奶粉的产品品质。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">太子乐奶粉咋样？</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">太子乐以绝佳</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">品质和品牌影响力，连续</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">5年全国销量超过10亿元，奠定国产婴幼儿配方奶粉主流品牌地位。太子乳业选址于哈尔滨市呼兰境内，此地位于松嫩平原，南临松花江，西傍呼兰河。太子乐从奶源到生产、销售的全过程对环境卫生要求相当高。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0000;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">太子乐乳业通过引进国内外一流的设备，精密的仪器测试，将质量控制贯彻到生产的每一个环节。太子乐奶粉怎么样？为了满足宝宝多样化的营养需求，太子乐为了保证给所有的宝宝吃到健康放心的太子乐奶粉，对所有的原料、半成品、成品每一批都会进行严格的检验，并制定了高于国家的内控标准，给太子乐的品质保障上了双重保险。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:12pt;text-indent:21pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">太子乐奶粉最新事件：</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">太子乐凭借过硬的产品质量，产品抽检全部合格，以及多个公益事业活动，企业被授予</span>“优秀新产品奖”、新浪育儿盛典社会公益践行品牌称号</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:微软雅黑;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">、铂金</span>100奶粉新秀奖等多项殊荣。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;font-size:12.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>','','','2016-12-20 09:22:58','','2','1','0');
