;\" /></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;position:static;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;position:static;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 观传统婚礼、看小猪赛跑、购天然土猪肉、认养小猪，与去年的巴山年猪节相比，今年的年猪节将更加突出巴山当地悠久的年猪文化，巴山年猪之夜文艺晚会也会为远道而来的客人展现不一样的节目亮点。</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 说到巴山年猪文化节，最受大家关注的当然就是“听音乐、吃百草、饮山泉、舔硒土”的巴山土猪。为贴合巴山年猪文化节的主体，突出自身执着于有机、绿色、纯天然、干净、安全、有品质的产品的特点，在今年的巴山年猪文化节上，作为嘉宾出席活动的好云淘商城，巧妙融入了生态有机的健康理念，将携手通江县巴山生态牧业科技有限公司，为广大市民献上“听音乐，饮溪水，舔硒土”的青峪生态有机猪肉。</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 为方便消费者购买优质放心的有机猪肉，目前“充值送年猪”等优惠活动已在好云淘商城顺势上线。会员在好云淘商城充值8888元，就可得到巴山有机年猪1头、好云淘商城现金券2664元及商城购物余额8888元。而经济实惠的鲜肉套餐和腊肉套餐，更是为广大消费者提前献上了丰厚的年货大餐。据悉，活动当天好云淘联合巴山牧业还会推出更大的惊喜！</p>\r\n</section></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;position:static;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;position:static;\"><img class=\"\" src=\"http://img.xiumi.us/xmi/ua/Lv5t/i/2431d22b529acd7b9667b9a953333dff-sz_413282.png@1l_640w.png\" data-ratio=\"0.6243316\" data-w=\"467\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;border:0px;vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;\" /></section></section><section class=\"Powered-by-XIUMI V5\" powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;position:static;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;position:static;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><p style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 一府三乡，大美通江，相信在巴山地区悠久的历史与深厚的文化底蕴的衬托下，今年第三届巴山年猪文化节，一定会带给大家不一样的视听盛宴！在这里，游客不仅可以一饱生态刨猪汤的口福，共享田园水乡的惬意，还能实实在在地领略一把巴山民俗风情的独特魅力。</p>\r\n<div><br />\r\n</div>\r\n</section></section></section></section></div>\r\n</section><section class=\"row tn-board-foot\" ng-show=\"isReady\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:-15px;margin-left:-15px;font-size:13px;color:#9c9d9f;margin-bottom:1.5em;font-family:\'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', Arial, sans-serif;line-height:normal;\"></section>','','','2016-12-23 01:05:51','','0','0','1');
