 Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\">微商、微信营销、社交电商、自媒体等诸多名词，并不是简单的是利用微信卖产品、卖服务。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\">这里要认识几个问题：</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\">1，营销，不等于销售。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\">2，社交电商，社交在前，商在后。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\">3，自媒体，在于自，把自己的朋友圈像运营一个媒体平台一样去做，“自”包装自己，体现价值，只要你有价值，才能吸引更多的价值。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\">好，认清了上述几个问题后，我们开始了解方法。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#0070c0;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#0070c0;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\">发布朋友圈内容的四个准则</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\">1，<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\">真实。真实的生活内容是朋友圈的本质</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;line-height:19.2pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;脱离的这些真实的生活内容，发布的都是广告，也就脱离了朋友圈基本的意义，也就与朋友圈里的人，产生了距离。</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\">??</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\">2，<span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\">信任。一切交易，都是建立在信任的基础之上。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;line-height:19.2pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;解决信任问题是前提，只要取得别人的信任，才有成交的基础，你所发布的内容，是为了提升你的信任度，而不是要影响你的信任度。你就知道什么内容该发，什么内容不该发了。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;line-height:19.2pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;line-height:19.2pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\">3，</span><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\">价值。一切交易，都来源于价值的互换。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;价值的体现，要体现两个方面，一方面是你本身的价值，?</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;line-height:19.2pt;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;line-height:19.2pt;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\">4，互动。是互动是营销的核心。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 有效的互动，能让陌生人变熟悉，能沟调动大家的积极性，能让更多人参与进来，能够给别人与你接触的机会。不管发什么内容，结尾总要留下互动的话题。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><strong style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#0070c0;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\">发布朋友圈内容的三个方向</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#0070c0;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\" />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#0070c0;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;\">一，个人展现</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#0070c0;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;\">1，真实生活</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#0070c0;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 朋友圈里，都愿意看到在微信背后这个人的真实生活一面。所以，发布真实的生活场景与个人感悟心得，是让别人了解的机会，也许取得信任的前提。同时，要充分现在个人魅力，另外，人们都喜欢，有情、有趣、有用、有品的人哦！</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#0070c0;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\" />\r\n</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#0070c0;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;\">2，专家形象</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#0070c0;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 你到医院，你是挂几元的普通号，还是花几十元挂专家号？我想真想看病，一定会挂专家号。为什么？因为我们信任专家。所以，不管你是做什么行业的，什么产品或者服务的，都要展现你专业的一面给你朋友圈里的人。提供给大家有价值的内容，有价值的经验，我想你收获的，不仅是大家对你的信任，同时你也博得了大家对你的认可和爱戴。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#0070c0;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\" />\r\n</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#0070c0;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;\">二，客户见证</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#0070c0;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;\">1，分享成交</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#0070c0;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 客户的咨询与购买的结果，通过朋友圈分享，让人知道你的成交的结果。人，都有从众心理，大家都在买的，大家都去的店，一定都是好的。通过分享，很多有意购买，但是没有确定的人，看到这样的信息，对他们就是一个肯定，一个定心丸，同时通过截图看到客户咨询的问题，你如实的解答，也接触了意向客户的疑虑。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#0070c0;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;\">2，分享反馈</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#0070c0;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 如果说到了分享成交的步骤后，一些意向客户，还在犹豫，那么分享已经成交客户的反馈，这将是给这部分人最好的答案。在整个内容当中，客户见证的分享，将会大大提升你的成交。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#0070c0;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\" />\r\n</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#0070c0;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;\">三，教育引导</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#0070c0;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 放大痛点，放大产品或者服务的价值，增加购买欲望。客户所购买的是你所给她/他带来的价值，能为她/他解决什么问题。你的内容，越是能够解开客户的伤口，越是让客户感到疼痛，你才能得到客户的认可。就像看病意向，大夫从来先不说治疗方案，都是先说你的病，是不是有什么反应，如果大夫说对了，说到了你的痛点了，他给你的治疗方案，你才认可。</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#0070c0;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#3e3e3e;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\" />\r\n</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\">听课 &nbsp;只是第一步，第二步是 &nbsp;提炼干货。第三步是 &nbsp;实践，第四步 &nbsp;总结，第五步 &nbsp;分享。五步执行完毕，才是学习的一个周期。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#0070c0;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;\">将文本收藏，实践之后，再看一遍，你的心得体会更多一些！</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\"><img data-ratio=\"1.1483312731767614\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"809\" data-s=\"300,640\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz_png/fxo9s6LRElCMld1ogUXicUPTm5VRsUUINLacrbk5b6Xjkc23tZhVibBtcJylAsX2dfOZaMk54w3kA1iaxvplTNicRQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" _src=\"https://mmbiz.qlogo.cn/mmbiz_png/fxo9s6LRElCMld1ogUXicUPTm5VRsUUINLacrbk5b6Xjkc23tZhVibBtcJylAsX2dfOZaMk54w3kA1iaxvplTNicRQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;height:auto !important;\" /><br style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;\" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;clear:both;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:medium;\">欢迎转载，但要表明出处，本篇文章来自于微信公众号：“王元龙”</p>\r\n<div><br />\r\n</div>','','','2016-12-30 10:54:33','','2','1','0');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('296','shixin','','531','2017010484520','小格雷S1重磅上市绿网天下进军高端学生机市场','搜狐媒体','','8','<span style=\"color:#484848;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:32.2px;\">元旦刚过，当各大手机厂商准备吹响2017新品首发号角的时候，绿网天下已经抢先推新，小格雷学生手机S1日前正式发布。</span><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;color:#484848;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:32.2px;\">　　笔者在淘宝、京东两个电商平台上看到这款神秘的小格雷S1的真容，如果说小格雷GP-50是以千元价格抢占低端学生机市场的话，S1时尚的外观和高端配置就足以说明它将面向中高端消费市场。</p>\r\n<center style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#484848;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:32.2px;\"><img alt=\"软文配图02\" border=\"1\" height=\"307\" src=\"http://invest.china.com.cn/quyu/uploadfile/2017/0103/20170103060514249.jpg\" width=\"553\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border:none;vertical-align:top;\" /></center><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;color:#484848;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:32.2px;\">　　小格雷S1配备了64位8核处理器、3GB内存，将给用户带来更强大的体验。外观上，S1有玫瑰金、香槟金、夜空黑三款颜色，流线超薄设计搭配金属后壳，时尚大方。后置1600万，前置800万高配摄像头，符合现在学生对手机拍照清晰度的苛刻要求。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;color:#484848;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:32.2px;\">　　学生专属功能方面，小格雷S1依然采用Green OS系统，家长可以对手机使用时间、内容、应用全方位管控，同时搭载专为学生设计的绿网浏览器和绿网应用市场，无疑S1成为一款让家长放心的手机。相比售价2k-3k的同类机型来说，小格雷S1仅售1998元，更具性价比。</p>\r\n<center style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;color:#484848;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:32.2px;\"><img alt=\"44\" border=\"1\" height=\"279\" src=\"http://invest.china.com.cn/quyu/uploadfile/2017/0103/20170103060515773.jpg\" width=\"553\" data-bd-imgshare-binded=\"1\" style=\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border:none;vertical-align:top;\" /></center><p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;color:#484848;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:32.2px;\">　　一直以来，绿网天下小格雷学生手机着重突出的是手机中的管控功能，相比其他品牌学生手机管控功能单一、简易的缺点，小格雷学生手机在管控方面一直有着比较明显的优势。但不得不承认，学习功能是学生手机中不可或缺的一部分，很多家长在给孩子买手机时，也非常重视学习资源方面的内容。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;color:#484848;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:32.2px;\">　　在小格雷学生手机GP-50中，学习资源大多是学习类APP，而小格雷S1的诞生，宣告绿网天下迈入学习内容行业大军。小格雷S1拥有超过290000份教学资源，实现小学、初中、高中9门学科全覆盖;同时精心筛选黄冈、西南师大等名校名师的40000多部教学视频课件，走到哪，“名师课堂”跟到哪;另外，还有300000多道全学习题库，280000条词条解析，11000份经典学案，资源全覆盖，庞大题库一站齐全……可以看出，绿网天下正加大学习资源的运营，以管控+内容+终端的形式，逐步完善自己的教育生态。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:0px;list-style:none;color:#484848;font-family:宋体;font-size:14px;line-height:32.2px;\">　　绿网天下S1究竟能否扎根学生市场，收获高端消费群体的认可还需时间考验。不过在快速迭代的智能终端行业，想让品牌获得更多的认可，还是需要从产品创新上做好功夫，小格雷S1无疑是一个很好的开始，让我们一起期待。</p>','广告','','2017-01-04 02:38:08','','3','1','0');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('297','我爱钓鱼','','516','2017010752517','棠果旅居被评为2016年度最具成长力创业项目','今日头条','http://www.toutiao.com/i6372753872875684353/','5','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">2017</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">第二届中国<span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span>新年峰会在北京亚洲大酒店举行。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:30pt;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170107134716_91243.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">棠果旅居<span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span>金东哲获得年度中国新锐<span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span>人物大奖现场分享棠果旅居品牌</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">据悉，本次大会邀请<span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span>位<span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span>轮融资的创业项目<span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span>和投资人参加，此外还有千位创业者参加大会。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:15pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;\">作为国内首个把</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\">“自由居<span lang=\"EN-US\">+</span>自由行”概念深耕到全球短租市场的品牌，</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">棠果旅居<span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span>金东哲</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\">受邀参加并</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">与近百位优秀的创投圈大佬分享干货。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:30pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;line-height:30px;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170107134747_17616.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">棠果旅居荣获年度创业“金鸥奖”<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">会上，棠果旅居<span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span>金东哲、中国<span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>巴菲特<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span>、国鸣投资董事长吴鸣霄、易一天使合伙人曹日辉、创新工场合伙人张鹰、优客工场执行合伙人高超等众多互联网创业新将老兵一起分享经验、交流心得。借势共享交流平台，推动资源整合、商业模式更新、人脉建立等实质推动创新创业发展的新场景。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:30pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;line-height:30px;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170107134810_45798.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">互联网创业新将老兵一起分享经验、交流心得<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">有人说，这是最好的时代，也是最糟糕的时代。互联网时代的交换更替瞬时万变。对于企业只有抓住时机，不停止创新，不辜负机遇。才会</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;\">快速实现自我颠覆，立足长青。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">本次大会得到了中国经济网、赛迪网、华商网、中国网、中原网、新京报、亿邦动力网、<span lang=\"EN-US\">36kr</span>、虎嗅、猎云网、品途商业评论、<span lang=\"EN-US\">MC</span>创投梦工厂、梅花财经、融资中国等<span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span>多家媒体的支持与关注报道。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:30pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;line-height:30px;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170107134832_39429.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">棠果旅居获得<span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span>年度最具成长力创业项目<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">棠果旅居<span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span>金东哲在接受采访时表示：</span><span style=\"font-size:15pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;\">棠果旅居作为好玩、时尚的一站式旅居共享平台，持续保持着品牌的新鲜与活力。在用户主权的旅行时代，推出人们期待的个性化、生活化的住宿和旅行产品，</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;\">用匠心的心态打造华人的“梦想”平台。</span><a name=\"_GoBack\"></a><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>','','','2017-01-07 01:49:20','','2','1','0');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('298','我爱钓鱼','','513','2017010754684','棠果旅居CEO金东哲获得年度中国新锐CEO人物大奖，受创投大咖热捧','网易客户端','http://c.m.163.com/news/a/CA6FV5EA0511C41A.html','8','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;\">2017</span><span style=\"font-size:15pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;\">第二届中国<span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span>新年峰会在北京亚洲大酒店举行。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:15pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170107135201_99519.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:0px;\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt;font-family:仿宋;\">棠果旅居<span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span>金东哲获得年度中国新锐<span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span>人物大奖现场分享棠果旅居品牌</span></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">据悉，本次大会邀请<span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span>位<span lang=\"EN-US\">A</span>轮融资的创业项目<span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span>和投资人参加，此外还有千位创业者参加大会。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:15pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;\">作为国内首个把</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\">“自由居<span lang=\"EN-US\">+</span>自由行”概念深耕到全球短租市场的品牌，</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">棠果旅居<span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span>金东哲</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;\">受邀参加并</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">与近百位优秀的创投圈大佬分享干货。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:30pt;line-height:150%;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\"><o:p>&nbsp;<img src=\"../../upload/20170107135328_38223.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">棠果旅居荣获年度创业“金鸥奖”<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">会上，棠果旅居<span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span>金东哲、中国<span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span>巴菲特<span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span>、国鸣投资董事长吴鸣霄、易一天使合伙人曹日辉、创新工场合伙人张鹰、优客工场执行合伙人高超等众多互联网创业新将老兵一起分享经验、交流心得。借势共享交流平台，推动资源整合、商业模式更新、人脉建立等实质推动创新创业发展的新场景。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:30pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;line-height:30px;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170107135230_23859.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">互联网创业新将老兵一起分享经验、交流心得<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">有人说，这是最好的时代，也是最糟糕的时代。互联网时代的交换更替瞬时万变。对于企业只有抓住时机，不停止创新，不辜负机遇。才会</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;\">快速实现自我颠覆，立足长青。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">本次大会得到了中国经济网、赛迪网、华商网、中国网、中原网、新京报、亿邦动力网、<span lang=\"EN-US\">36kr</span>、虎嗅、猎云网、品途商业评论、<span lang=\"EN-US\">MC</span>创投梦工厂、梅花财经、融资中国等<span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span>多家媒体的支持与关注报道。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:30pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:仿宋;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;line-height:30px;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170107135254_16127.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:24.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">棠果旅居获得<span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span>年度最具成长力创业项目<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:30.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;line-height:150%;\"><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\">棠果旅居<span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span>金东哲在接受采访时表示：</span><span style=\"font-size:15pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;\">棠果旅居作为好玩、时尚的一站式旅居共享平台，持续保持着品牌的新鲜与活力。在用户主权的旅行时代，推出人们期待的个性化、生活化的住宿和旅行产品，</span><span style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;\">用匠心的心态打造华人的“梦想”平台。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:15.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:仿宋;mso-bidi-font-family:Arial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>','','','2017-01-07 01:53:51','','2','1','0');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('299','shixin','','517','2017011225361','2017学生手机市场又迎高端机','新浪看点','','8','<p style=\"border:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:26px 0px 0px;font-size:14px;color:#333333;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;line-height:26px;\">刚过去的2016年对于各大手机制造商来说，无疑是竞争白热化的一年。如果说华为、中兴等品牌已经打入国际市场份额，挑战苹果、三星等领头地位的话，我们不妨放眼国内智能手机细分市场，除了各方在配置、价格上的拉锯战，智能机市场还有什么亮点值得我们眼前一亮?答案，可能就是学生专用手机。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:26px 0px 0px;font-size:14px;color:#333333;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;line-height:26px;\">　　2016年，学生专用手机进入了消费者视野。学生专用手机并不是传统意义上所谓的评价好、配置性价比高，适合学生购买和使用的手机。而是以学习、管控功能为主打，一方面帮助家长监督孩子用手机，另一方面转移手机娱乐功能性，赋予手机移动信息化教育工具的作用。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:26px 0px 0px;font-size:14px;color:#333333;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;line-height:26px;text-align:center;\"><img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20170111/74832da844ba4c9baeb44e106beb4469_th.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:0px;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:0px;color:transparent;max-width:600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:26px 0px 0px;font-size:14px;color:#333333;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;line-height:26px;\">　　相比其他电教品牌推出的学生手机，软件起家的绿网天下可谓是先行抓住了消费者的购买动机，小格雷S0在2016年的销售表现让人惊艳。不难想象，学生没有消费能力，家长才是购买学生手机的主力群体。在家长的角度，最担心孩子玩手机不受控，因此，绿网天下研发十余年的管控技术可谓势在必得，完全符合家长的购买需求，这也是小格雷S0热销的深层原因。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:26px 0px 0px;font-size:14px;color:#333333;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;line-height:26px;\">　　就在2016年的年尾，外观更时尚、定位更加高端的小格雷S1抢先上市。这款手机主要在两方面进行了提升，一个是手机的外观和配置上。香槟金、玫瑰金、夜空黑，三款经典机身色，工艺斟酌品质立现。配置上，无论是3G+32G的内存，还是1600W+800W的摄像头像素，都体现了学生高端机的属性。另一方面，小格雷S1植入了大量的学习资源，充分打通管控+学习两条学生主线的功能点，290000份教学资源，小学、初中、高中9门学科全覆盖。300000多道全学习题库，280000条词条解析，庞大题库一站齐全。</p>\r\n<p style=\"border:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:26px 0px 0px;font-size:14px;color:#333333;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;line-height:26px;text-align:center;\"><img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20170111/072d11c0c16b4da0b279935bfec3a523_th.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:0px;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:0px;color:transparent;max-width:600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:26px 0px 0px;font-size:14px;color:#333333;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;line-height:26px;text-align:center;\"><img src=\"http://img.mp.itc.cn/upload/20170111/09f4d6e3f1d948a78febfbddf535ee80_th.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border:0px;margin:0px;padding:0px;font-size:0px;color:transparent;max-width:600px;\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"border:0px;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:26px 0px 0px;font-size:14px;color:#333333;word-wrap:break-word;font-family:宋体;line-height:26px;\">　　2017年，究竟小格雷S1能否在学生手机市场取得不俗表现还不得而知。然而我们不得不再次认识到，学生专属手机的核心功能，是时间管控和网址过滤技术。就这一领域而言，绿网天下小格雷的功能点是相对全面的，近5亿条的网址库也充分体现了过滤技术的沉淀。领先的管控系统，加上高端机的硬件配置，小格雷S1应该能走得更高更远。</p>','','','2017-01-12 10:46:56','','0','0','1');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('300','我爱钓鱼','','513','2017011918791','棠果在泰国大受追捧加速东南亚市场布局','网易客户端','http://c.m.163.com/news/a/CB5NGCVG05228LNH.html','8','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">【棠果旅居</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TANGO</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">】继在泰国曼谷举办的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">年亚洲旅游年度风尚大典</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">NowTravelAsia\r\nAwards 2016</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">上精彩亮相之后，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">TANGO</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">得到了来自泰国从泰国国家旅游局到大住宿业的全面关注，这样一个以互联网基因和资源分享，精彩旅居为概念的品牌得到了泰国产业链的极大兴趣。随着棠果旅居</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">APP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">的客户数量超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">500</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">万，越来越多的粉丝对泰国市场的非标住宿房源和旅游攻略提出了需求和强烈的意愿，为此，棠果旅居总裁金东哲先生在得到泰方诚意邀请的情况下，迅速进行了泰国市场的布局。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170119174329_60303.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">日，亚洲旅游中国区</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">泰中旅游酒店友好协会创始人兼秘书长</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">棠果旅居泰国市场高级顾问夏彬彬先生代表金东哲总裁拜会了【泰国班德拉酒店集团</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">BANDARA GROUP</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">】，集团财务总监</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">SermsriSayasit</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">女士以及集团首席商务官</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ApichatChowadee</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">先生做了热情的接待，会晤期间，泰国班德拉酒店集团特别向棠果旅居表示了将以曼谷班德拉酒店作为基地，推进【棠果泰国办事处】的成立，同时，表示泰国班德拉集团旗下物业中的海滩别墅、度假屋等非标特色产品将最大限度的配合棠果旅居在泰国的业务推进。夏彬彬先生受金东哲总裁的委托，向班德拉酒店集团赠送了棠果的新年礼物以及介绍了棠果在国内的精彩布局以及从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2017</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">年开始将泰国作为主力市场进行推进的极大意愿。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170119174339_10285.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\r\n<!--[endif]--></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">日上午，受棠果旅居总裁金东哲先生的委托，亚洲旅游中国区</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">泰中旅游酒店友好协会创始人兼秘书长</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">/</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;\">棠果旅居泰国市场高级顾问夏彬彬先生在曼谷的四面佛，代表棠果人，向中国大住宿业的行业伙伴、广大客户以及在泰国酒店和非标住宿业中的所有朋友送上了虔诚的祝福，期待棠果旅游泰国办事处的落地启动。棠果泰国办事处（筹）初步选址</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 8FL, 75/1 SaladaengSoi 1, Saladaeng Road, Silom, Bangkok 10500\r\nThailand. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>','','','2017-01-19 05:44:42','','2','1','0');
