INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('302','我爱钓鱼','','519','2017012327630','棠果1亿红包新春重磅来袭出游旅行省钱啦','一点资讯','','10','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#333333;\">你吃了最正宗的北京烤鸭，看了气势宏伟的秦始皇兵马俑，登上了东方明珠塔，去了古迹，也看了熊猫，以为这就是旅游了？错，住在棠果的深院古巷，才叫深度游！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;color:#333333;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"font-size:19px;line-height:27px;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170123094518_78126.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:28.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.0;\"><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#333333;\">棠果作为旅行民宿热门预订平台，为全球华人提供民宿、公寓、别墅、当地人文旅行预订服务，目前已覆盖国内外近</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;color:#333333;\">300</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#333333;\">座城市，上线房源达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:14.0pt;color:#333333;\">120000</span><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin;color:#333333;\">间，不论是常规民宿还是带有民族风情的特色民宿、亦或是个性化十足的树屋、历史悠久的老宅、精心设计改造后的屋舍，棠果都能给你绝对的满足。</span><