e&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">10</span><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">万间房屋，拥有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">300</span><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">万会员。在中国不断进行旅行社收购，实现了快速增长。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">2016</span><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">10</span><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">月，正式开启海外市场，为全球华人定制一站式旅行服务。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:OpenSans;mso-bidi-font-family:OpenSans;color:#262626;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"../../upload/20170213102154_83677.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">棠果在日本和韩国分别成立了全额出资子公司，注册资金分别为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">1</span><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">亿日元和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">1</span><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">亿韩币。日韩棠果</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">APP</span><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">及网站推广计划将于近期开通，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">2</span><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">月底正式召开日韩发布会。</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"> </span><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">日韩市场的全面开发，不仅提升更多华人在日韩的旅居体验，更是希望让更多的韩国人到中国消费，目前已经完成高尔夫旅游团队及高端团队的积累。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"../../upload/20170213102204_18300.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family:opensans;mso-hansi-font-family:OpenSans;mso-bidi-font-family:OpenSans;color:#262626;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">虽同样是共享经济，棠果和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:OpenSans;mso-bidi-font-family:OpenSans;color:#262626;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">Uber</span><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family:OpenSans;mso-hansi-font-family:OpenSans;mso-bidi-font-family:OpenSans;color:#262626;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">等其他共享经济不同，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:opensans;mso-bidi-font-family:OpenSans;color:#262626;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">Uber</span><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family:OpenSans;mso-hansi-font-family:OpenSans;mso-bidi-font-family:OpenSans;color:#262626;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">模式的全球化扩张，对本地化要求非常高，而棠果则是本地用户的境外游，是真正的全球化生意。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:OpenSans;mso-bidi-font-family:OpenSans;color:#262626;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;text-indent:21pt;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170213102219_96437.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:21.0pt;\"><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family:opensans;mso-hansi-font-family:OpenSans;mso-bidi-font-family:OpenSans;color:#262626;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">住宿和旅游是重要的生活场景与数据价值来源，一方面，随着棠果上房客和游客数量越来越多，平台可以采集到更加多样的用户数据，市场细分研究显示，平台拥有的多样数据的价值。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:OpenSans;mso-bidi-font-family:OpenSans;color:#262626;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family:opensans;mso-hansi-font-family:OpenSans;mso-bidi-font-family:OpenSans;color:#262626;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\">另一方面，如果将平台现有的服务与智能家居、增强现实、物联网等场景数据挖掘工具进行整合，就可以对用户数据做深度挖掘与利用，为棠果开拓更多产业链商业模式方面的扩展路径。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;helveticaneue&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Helveticaneue&quot;;color:#424242;mso-font-kerning:0pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"left\"></p>','','','2017-02-13 10:23:10','','2','1','1');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('314','我爱钓鱼','','517','2017021360004','棠果全面进军韩国日本市场，加速全球化布局','新浪看点','http://k.sina.cn/article_5926120321_161396b81001001a1x.html','8','<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;\">月<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>日，棠果旅居创始人兼<span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span>金东哲与负责棠果韩国市场开发的申社长以及负责日本市场开发的桂总，召开了韩日战略合作会议，全面启动韩国和日本市场的开发，也标志着棠果已全面开启韩国和日本市场。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170213142455_71778.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170213142506_88272.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;\">目前，棠果在韩国和日本分别成立了全额出资子公司。韩日市场的全面开发，不仅提升更多华人在韩日的旅居体验，更是希望让更多的外国人到中国消费，据悉，近期将有大量韩国高尔夫旅游团队及高端旅游团队跟着棠果游中国。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170213142517_22752.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;\">来自中国旅游研究院的最新数据，相比<span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span>年的<span lang=\"EN-US\">1.17</span>亿人次，<span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span>年中国的出境游规模同比增长<span lang=\"EN-US\">4.3%</span>，达到<span lang=\"EN-US\">1.22</span>亿，这一数字，相当于整个日本的人口，我国已经成为泰国、韩国、日本等多个国家的第一大入境旅游客源地。但与将近<span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span>亿的人口基数相比，这一数字仍有极大的上升空间，换言之，出境游发展依然潜力无穷。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170213142539_23447.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;\">不同于以往走马观花赶行程的旅行方式，中国大陆旅游者越来越倾向于选择更深入、更便利、更安全稳定、更热情友好、自然与生活环境更好的目的地。出境旅游已成为衡量中国城市家庭和年轻人幸福度的一大标准。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;\">出境游俨然已成为各大巨头和创业者的目标，试图分的一块蛋糕。在这一大潮流下，专注华人旅居市场的棠果，敏锐的捕捉到了这一趋势，适时进军海外市场。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170213142552_24658.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;\">棠果传达出的不仅仅是一种旅行方式，更是一种生活态度。棠果整合各大热门目的地丰富的资源，用年轻人喜欢的方式呈现出来，喜欢个性化、新鲜感、高品质旅行体验的用户将在棠果体验到传统大众游无法实现的私人定制出行体验。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170213142640_42777.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170213142654_41989.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;\">致力于打造华人出境一站式旅居平台，棠果从已经深耕<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>年的住宿入手，扩展到旅游中所涉及到的方方面面，与一些成熟的平台对接，帮助出境用户更加智能高效的连接当地的生活服务，包括接机、厨师、保姆、导游、票务预订等服务。目前，用户在棠果所能体验到的服务已经基本涵盖吃、住、行、游、购、娱、导等全面的旅游与生活需求，实现掌上一站式服务。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170213142710_55911.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170213142739_12356.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;\">未来，棠果将继续扩大海外市场，进军欧洲、美洲，逐步与英国、意大利、德国等多个国家签署战略合作协议，在整合营销及服务体系上达成深度合作。多维度深耕目的地资源，成为出境旅行新标杆。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>','','','2017-02-13 02:28:16','','2','1','0');
INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('315','我爱钓鱼','','515','2017021360004','棠果全面进军韩国日本市场，加速全球化布局','天天快报','http://kuaibao.qq.com/s/20170213A04YBH00','5','<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;\">月<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>日，棠果旅居创始人兼<span lang=\"EN-US\">CEO</span>金东哲与负责棠果韩国市场开发的申社长以及负责日本市场开发的桂总，召开了韩日战略合作会议，全面启动韩国和日本市场的开发，也标志着棠果已全面开启韩国和日本市场。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170213142455_71778.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170213142506_88272.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;\">目前，棠果在韩国和日本分别成立了全额出资子公司。韩日市场的全面开发，不仅提升更多华人在韩日的旅居体验，更是希望让更多的外国人到中国消费，据悉，近期将有大量韩国高尔夫旅游团队及高端旅游团队跟着棠果游中国。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170213142517_22752.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;\">来自中国旅游研究院的最新数据，相比<span lang=\"EN-US\">2015</span>年的<span lang=\"EN-US\">1.17</span>亿人次，<span lang=\"EN-US\">2016</span>年中国的出境游规模同比增长<span lang=\"EN-US\">4.3%</span>，达到<span lang=\"EN-US\">1.22</span>亿，这一数字，相当于整个日本的人口，我国已经成为泰国、韩国、日本等多个国家的第一大入境旅游客源地。但与将近<span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span>亿的人口基数相比，这一数字仍有极大的上升空间，换言之，出境游发展依然潜力无穷。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170213142539_23447.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;\">不同于以往走马观花赶行程的旅行方式，中国大陆旅游者越来越倾向于选择更深入、更便利、更安全稳定、更热情友好、自然与生活环境更好的目的地。出境旅游已成为衡量中国城市家庭和年轻人幸福度的一大标准。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;\">出境游俨然已成为各大巨头和创业者的目标，试图分的一块蛋糕。在这一大潮流下，专注华人旅居市场的棠果，敏锐的捕捉到了这一趋势，适时进军海外市场。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170213142552_24658.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;\">棠果传达出的不仅仅是一种旅行方式，更是一种生活态度。棠果整合各大热门目的地丰富的资源，用年轻人喜欢的方式呈现出来，喜欢个性化、新鲜感、高品质旅行体验的用户将在棠果体验到传统大众游无法实现的私人定制出行体验。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170213142640_42777.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170213142654_41989.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;\">致力于打造华人出境一站式旅居平台，棠果从已经深耕<span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span>年的住宿入手，扩展到旅游中所涉及到的方方面面，与一些成熟的平台对接，帮助出境用户更加智能高效的连接当地的生活服务，包括接机、厨师、保姆、导游、票务预订等服务。目前，用户在棠果所能体验到的服务已经基本涵盖吃、住、行、游、购、娱、导等全面的旅游与生活需求，实现掌上一站式服务。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170213142710_55911.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170213142739_12356.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;微软雅黑&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:微软雅黑;\">未来，棠果将继续扩大海外市场，进军欧洲、美洲，逐步与英国、意大利、德国等多个国家签署战略合作协议，在整合营销及服务体系上达成深度合作。多维度深耕目的地资源，成为出境旅行新标杆。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>','','','2017-02-13 02:28:16','','2','1','0');
