INSERT INTO ruanwen_info VALUES('366','我爱钓鱼','','515','2017022022084','2017棠果：全方位加深中葡旅游战略合作','天天快报','http://kuaibao.qq.com/s/20170220A02SQ300','5','<p class=\"duanluo\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:16px 0px 0px;text-align:justify;word-break:break-all;color:#4c4c4c;font-family:微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft yahei&quot;, Tahoma, Verdana, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:17px;\">2 月14日，葡萄牙国际贸易主席Bernardo在棠果国际事业部总监Ken的陪同下考察了棠果，就部分具体产业项目进行沟通对接，希望达成中葡旅游战略合作。</p>\r\n<div class=\"pic-video\" style=\"margin:12px auto 0px;padding:0px;position:relative;color:#4c4c4c;font-family:微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft yahei&quot;, Tahoma, Verdana, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:17px;\"><article style=\"position:relative;\"><img src=\"http://p0.ifengimg.com/pmop/2017/0218/228DC285515CC20A9682B09045A09862F93FB830_size379_w795_h527.png\" style=\"text-align:center;border-width:1px 0px;border-top-style:solid;border-right-style:initial;border-bottom-style:solid;border-left-style:initial;border-top-color:#ececec;border-right-color:initial;border-bottom-color:#ececec;border-left-color:initial;border-image:initial;display:block;width:622px;\" /></article></div>\r\n<p class=\"duanluo\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:16px 0px 0px;text-align:justify;word-break:break-all;color:#4c4c4c;font-family:微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft yahei&quot;, Tahoma, Verdana, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:17px;\">在棠果公司总部， Bernardo 对棠果企业进行了参观，并多方面了解了棠果业务，国际事业部总监 ken 也对 Bernardo 详细介绍了棠果的发展历程。交谈中， Bernardo 表示出对中国文化的浓厚兴趣，对于棠果平台的发展速度大赞不已，让世界各国用户通过棠果这个平台感受到中国的渊源文化。</p>\r\n<div class=\"pic-video\" style=\"margin:12px auto 0px;padding:0px;position:relative;color:#4c4c4c;font-family:微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft yahei&quot;, Tahoma, Verdana, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:17px;\"><article style=\"position:relative;\"><img src=\"http://p0.ifengimg.com/pmop/2017/0218/A42567A25752892A29CF47D8DA7B3CE5F0C60A16_size580_w806_h537.png\" style=\"border-width:1px 0px;border-top-style:solid;border-right-style:initial;border-bottom-style:solid;border-left-style:initial;border-top-color:#ececec;border-right-color:initial;border-bottom-color:#ececec;border-left-color:initial;border-image:initial;display:block;width:622px;\" /></article></div>\r\n<div class=\"pic-video\" style=\"margin:12px auto 0px;padding:0px;position:relative;color:#4c4c4c;font-family:微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft yahei&quot;, Tahoma, Verdana, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:17px;\"><article style=\"position:relative;\"><img src=\"http://p0.ifengimg.com/pmop/2017/0218/1A00A5E148CE20168B50D208F93E2AB5E74B80DF_size615_w801_h531.png\" style=\"border-width:1px 0px;border-top-style:solid;border-right-style:initial;border-bottom-style:solid;border-left-style:initial;border-top-color:#ececec;border-right-color:initial;border-bottom-color:#ececec;border-left-color:initial;border-image:initial;display:block;width:622px;\" /></article></div>\r\n<p class=\"duanluo\" style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;padding:16px 0px 0px;text-align:justify;word-break:break-all;color:#4c4c4c;font-family:微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft yahei&quot;, Tahoma, Verdana, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:17px;\">Bernardo 说，棠果品牌的个性会有助于加快棠果海外旅居市场的拓展，Bernardo也将通过与葡萄牙旅游局的接洽为棠果在跨境旅游方面起到开山之力。协助棠果在境外签证及注册用户上实现高速增长，助力棠果全球化发展。希望此次棠果携手葡萄牙President主席能为两国旅客打造优质独特的世界顶级旅游体验。</p>\r\n<div class=\"pic-video\" style=\"margin:12px auto 0px;padding:0px;position:relative;color:#4c4c4c;font-family:微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft yahei&quot;, Tahoma, Verdana, Arial,sans-serif;font-size:17px;\"><article style=\"position:relative;\"><img src=\"http://p0.ifengimg.com/pmop/2017/0218/795AF4C2F1E3FDF17DEE68E03BA42404C495625C_size573_w796_h526.png\" style=\"border-width:1px 0px;border-top-style:solid;border-right-style:initial;border-bottom-style:solid;border-left-style:initial;border-top-color:#ececec;border-right-color:initial;border-bottom-color:#ececec;border-left-color:initial;border-image:initial;display:block;width:622px;\" /></article></div>','','','2017-02-20 10:58:35','','2','1','0');
