"><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape id=\"_x0000_i1026\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style=\"width:403.5pt;height:268.5pt;\">  <v:imagedata src=\"file:///C:\\DOCUME~1\\ADMINI~1\\LOCALS~1\\Temp\\msohtml1\\01\\clip_image003.jpg\" o:title=\"\" /> </v:shape><![endif]--><!--[if !vml]--><img width=\"538\" height=\"358\" src=\"file:///C:/DOCUME~1/ADMINI~1/LOCALS~1/Temp/msohtml1/01/clip_image004.jpg\" v:shapes=\"_x0000_i1026\" /><!--[endif]--></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">没想到节目组是憋着放大招，在情人节录制现场传来的剧照里，舞台上居然站着蔡明！在女笑星这个级别上，近年来《欢乐喜剧人》一手捧红的贾玲，算是风头正劲，但是跟蔡姐姐比资历还是差不少火候。跟蔡明同时代女笑星当然也有，但是在喜剧市场的活跃度都远不及她了。早些年蔡明跟郭达的黄金搭档留下大量经典小品，到现在几乎没人超越，后来在电视喜剧里塑造的马大姐也是深入人心、经久不衰。进入新时代，蔡姐也得心应手地玩转潮流文化。作为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">61</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">年生人，风姿不减的蔡明居然连着几年春晚，给自己贴出了一个“美艳毒舌奶奶”的人设标签，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;\">年</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#333333;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">“都是千年的狐狸，你跟我玩什么聊斋啊？”仍是金句，今年“颜值越高责任越大”又成爆款。从各种角度上说，蔡明都是当下独尊的喜剧女王。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family:Arial;color:#333333;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>','','','2017-02-21 05:19:27','','0','0','1');
