mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　　青汁就是在大麦麦苗长到</span>20-30<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">公分最营养的时候烘干磨的粉</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">　　【三里人家大麦若叶青汁】主要功效有：</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　　</span>1<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，排毒：通便秘、除口气、清肠。</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　　</span>2<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，瘦身：瘦小肚腩，啤酒肚控重、排油脂 。</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　　</span>3<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，养颜：祛痘、淡斑、提亮肤色。</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">　　</span>4<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，调节内分泌：痛经、胸胀、腰酸、宫寒、月经不调等。</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.7500pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">5,<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">解酒，护肝，降三高。</span></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.7500pt;\"><img width=\"532\" height=\"931\" src=\"file:///C:\\Users\\dell\\AppData\\Local\\Temp\\ksohtml\\wps73.tmp.png\" /><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">青汁可以很好的弥补较少吃青菜人群的营养平衡。而且一般的青汁都易于食用、可与多种食物搭配。像颗粒型的小袋包装携带方便的同时食用方法丰富，如溶解在牛奶里，就成了类似奶茶类的柔和饮品，还可以放入咖啡、或者清汤里面，美味健康的同时又很便捷。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.7500pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">当然最本质的是离不开已被科学验证了的本身具有的多种美容、健康功效。日本著名艺人船越英一郎就曾透露自己每天都会喝一杯青汁。也有一些日本艺人在出美容书时表示每天喝一杯青汁就像必修课一样。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.7500pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">不仅如此，现在青汁也在亚洲的一些国家和地区、慢慢盛行，或许不久的将来这股</span>“青汁风”也会刮到你身边。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.7500pt;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\">随着生产制作水平的进步，青汁在保证原本的营养功效时口感也越变越好，加上一些专门机构对青汁的研究、普及。因此大人、小孩、老人、艺人等全民饮用青汁已是一种风潮。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#ff0000;font-size:20pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">招商微信：</span>lan 140813</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;color:#ff0000;font-size:20pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#ff0000;font-size:20pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">加盟电话：</span>18559800508</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;color:#ff0000;font-size:20pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:27.7500pt;\"><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#ff0000;font-size:20pt;\">三里人家合伙人小蓝</span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;color:#ff0000;font-size:20pt;\">&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;font-size