span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\">“歌秀”、“绿中医师”、“藏王”等“一洗黑”产品，在</span><a href=\"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E9%83%A8&amp;tn=44039180_cpr&amp;fenlei=mv6quAkxTZn0IZRqIHckPjm4nH00T1YYPW9-ujNWn1RsPjF-nW640ZwV5Hcvrjm3rH6sPfKWUMw85HfYnjn4nH6sgvPsT6KdThsqpZwYTjCEQLGCpyw9Uz4Bmy-bIi4WUvYETgN-TLwGUv3EnH0YPWmdrjb1nHc4PHfvP1m4rf\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#000000;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">卫生部</span></span></a><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">备案的</span></span><a href=\"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E6%89%B9%E5%8F%B7&amp;tn=44039180_cpr&amp;fenlei=mv6quAkxTZn0IZRqIHckPjm4nH00T1YYPW9-ujNWn1RsPjF-nW640ZwV5Hcvrjm3rH6sPfKWUMw85HfYnjn4nH6sgvPsT6KdThsqpZwYTjCEQLGCpyw9Uz4Bmy-bIi4WUvYETgN-TLwGUv3EnH0YPWmdrjb1nHc4PHfvP1m4rf\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#000000;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">生产批号</span></span></a><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">却是发给染发膏的，到底是打着洗发水的幌子卖的实质是染发膏，还是根本在说洗发根治白发的谎言？</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"pre\" style=\"margin-top:7.5pt;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a href=\"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=%E4%B8%AD%E5%B1%B1%E4%B8%89%E9%99%A2&amp;tn=44039180_cpr&amp;fenlei=mv6quAkxTZn0IZRqIHckPjm4nH00T1YYPW9-ujNWn1RsPjF-nW640ZwV5Hcvrjm3rH6sPfKWUMw85HfYnjn4nH6sgvPsT6KdThsqpZwYTjCEQLGCpyw9Uz4Bmy-bIi4WUvYETgN-TLwGUv3EnH0YPWmdrjb1nHc4PHfvP1m4rf\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#000000;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">中山三院</span></span></a><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">皮肤科主任、</span></span><a href=\"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=%E5%8D%8E%E5%8D%97%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%BA&amp;tn=44039180_cpr&amp;fenlei=mv6quAkxTZn0IZRqIHckPjm4nH00T1YYPW9-ujNWn1RsPjF-nW640ZwV5Hcvrjm3rH6sPfKWUMw85HfYnjn4nH6sgvPsT6KdThsqpZwYTjCEQLGCpyw9Uz4Bmy-bIi4WUvYETgN-TLwGUv3EnH0YPWmdrjb1nHc4PHfvP1m4rf\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#000000;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">华南地区</span></span></a><a href=\"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=%E5%8D%AB%E7%94%9F%E9%83%A8&amp;tn=44039180_cpr&amp;fenlei=mv6quAkxTZn0IZRqIHckPjm4nH00T1YYPW9-ujNWn1RsPjF-nW640ZwV5Hcvrjm3rH6sPfKWUMw85HfYnjn4nH6sgvPsT6KdThsqpZwYTjCEQLGCpyw9Uz4Bmy-bIi4WUvYETgN-TLwGUv3EnH0YPWmdrjb1nHc4PHfvP1m4rf\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#000000;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">卫生部</span></span></a><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">化妆品皮肤病诊断机构负责人赖维主任医师在接受记者采访时称，市面上流行的</span>“一洗黑”多少含有染发剂的成分，它们正是通过少量染发剂的长期使用来达到慢慢染黑头发的目的，使用这些“一洗黑”洗发产品，实际上就是在染发。一些不明就里的消费者和白发患者被偷换概念的销售方式欺骗，有的皮肤敏感者甚至因被蒙骗而使用“一洗黑”后，出现</span><a href=\"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=%E8%BF%87%E6%95%8F%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%AE%E7%82%8E&amp;tn=44039180_cpr&amp;fenlei=mv6quAkxTZn0IZRqIHckPjm4nH00T1YYPW9-ujNWn1RsPjF-nW640ZwV5Hcvrjm3rH6sPfKWUMw85HfYnjn4nH6sgvPsT6KdThsqpZwYTjCEQLGCpyw9Uz4Bmy-bIi4WUvYETgN-TLwGUv3EnH0YPWmdrjb1nHc4PHfvP1m4rf\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#000000;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">过敏性皮炎</span></span></a><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">。他称，门诊就发现过是一位</span>40来岁的女性，由于使用了某品牌的“一洗黑”产品，头部出现了湿疹样改变，还起了水泡，苦不堪言。赖维主任还称，很多“一洗黑”产品实质只是换了名字和包装的染发膏，使用的也是染发膏的</span><a href=\"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%A7%E6%89%B9%E5%8F%B7&amp;tn=44039180_cpr&amp;fenlei=mv6quAkxTZn0IZRqIHckPjm4nH00T1YYPW9-ujNWn1RsPjF-nW640ZwV5Hcvrjm3rH6sPfKWUMw85HfYnjn4nH6sgvPsT6KdThsqpZwYTjCEQLGCpyw9Uz4Bmy-bIi4WUvYETgN-TLwGUv3EnH0YPWmdrjb1nHc4PHfvP1m4rf\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#000000;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">生产批号</span></span></a><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">，这是不合法的。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"pre\" style=\"margin-top:7.5pt;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">使用不合法的产品出了问题，消费者也没有保障。更严重的是，这些</span>“一洗黑”为欺骗消费者而称不标明实际的染发剂成分（如“</span><a href=\"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=%E5%AF%B9%E8%8B%AF%E4%BA%8C%E8%83%BA&amp;tn=44039180_cpr&amp;fenlei=mv6quAkxTZn0IZRqIHckPjm4nH00T1YYPW9-ujNWn1RsPjF-nW640ZwV5Hcvrjm3rH6sPfKWUMw85HfYnjn4nH6sgvPsT6KdThsqpZwYTjCEQLGCpyw9Uz4Bmy-bIi4WUvYETgN-TLwGUv3EnH0YPWmdrjb1nHc4PHfvP1m4rf\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:微