%BB%E9%99%A2&amp;tn=44039180_cpr&amp;fenlei=mv6quAkxTZn0IZRqIHckPjm4nH00T1YYPW9-ujNWn1RsPjF-nW640ZwV5Hcvrjm3rH6sPfKWUMw85HfYnjn4nH6sgvPsT6KdThsqpZwYTjCEQLGCpyw9Uz4Bmy-bIi4WUvYETgN-TLwGUv3EnH0YPWmdrjb1nHc4PHfvP1m4rf\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#000000;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">广州军区总医院</span></span></a><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">皮肤科主任</span></span><a href=\"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=%E6%9D%A8%E6%85%A7%E5%85%B0&amp;tn=44039180_cpr&amp;fenlei=mv6quAkxTZn0IZRqIHckPjm4nH00T1YYPW9-ujNWn1RsPjF-nW640ZwV5Hcvrjm3rH6sPfKWUMw85HfYnjn4nH6sgvPsT6KdThsqpZwYTjCEQLGCpyw9Uz4Bmy-bIi4WUvYETgN-TLwGUv3EnH0YPWmdrjb1nHc4PHfvP1m4rf\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#000000;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">杨慧兰</span></span></a><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">称，目前没听说过洗头能让头发变黑的，除非洗头水中含有染发成分。她指出，由于洗发水用的是妆字号，当其含有染发剂时浓度更不受控制，为了显效，可能使用很高浓度的染发剂，何况把染发剂当洗发水一样频繁地使用，当人体对这些染发剂代谢有剩余时，对健康会有一定负面影响，对特殊体质的人的影响更大。她还强调，目前除了中药的何首乌和</span></span><a href=\"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=%E7%BB%B4%E7%94%9F%E7%B4%A0B5&amp;tn=44039180_cpr&amp;fenlei=mv6quAkxTZn0IZRqIHckPjm4nH00T1YYPW9-ujNWn1RsPjF-nW640ZwV5Hcvrjm3rH6sPfKWUMw85HfYnjn4nH6sgvPsT6KdThsqpZwYTjCEQLGCpyw9Uz4Bmy-bIi4WUvYETgN-TLwGUv3EnH0YPWmdrjb1nHc4PHfvP1m4rf\"><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#000000;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">维生素</span>B5</span></a><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">对白发治疗有些许辅助作用外，还没办法明显改善白发。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"pre\" style=\"margin-top:7.5pt;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><a href=\"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=%E5%B9%BF%E5%B7%9E%E5%86%9B%E5%8C%BA%E6%80%BB%E5%8C%BB%E9%99%A2&amp;tn=44039180_cpr&amp;fenlei=mv6quAkxTZn0IZRqIHckPjm4nH00T1YYPW9-ujNWn1RsPjF-nW640ZwV5Hcvrjm3rH6sPfKWUMw85HfYnjn4nH6sgvPsT6KdThsqpZwYTjCEQLGCpyw9Uz4Bmy-bIi4WUvYETgN-TLwGUv3EnH0YPWmdrjb1nHc4PHfvP1m4rf\"><b><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#000000;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">广州军区总医院</span></span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">皮肤科另一位医生刘仲荣副主任医师</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">基于</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">临床很多病</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">例</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">发现</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">：</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">无论是</span></span></b><a href=\"https://www.baidu.com/s?wd=%E5%B0%91%E7%99%BD%E5%8F%91&amp;tn=44039180_cpr&amp;fenlei=mv6quAkxTZn0IZRqIHckPjm4nH00T1YYPW9-ujNWn1RsPjF-nW640ZwV5Hcvrjm3rH6sPfKWUMw85HfYnjn4nH6sgvPsT6KdThsqpZwYTjCEQLGCpyw9Uz4Bmy-bIi4WUvYETgN-TLwGUv3EnH0YPWmdrjb1nHc4PHfvP1m4rf\"><b><span class=\"15\" style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;color:#000000;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">少白发</span></span></b></a><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">还是自然变白的头发，成因都一样。</span></span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\"pre\" style=\"margin-top:7.5pt;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">由于我们的黑头发都是由毛囊里的黑素细胞产生黑素小体后，渗入毛囊角质而使头发显现出黑色，当黑素细胞受破坏或黑小体的质或量减少，发色就变白。他强调，对于白发目前全球仍无根治方法，只能通过染发或毛发移植（将能长出黑发的毛囊移植到长白发处）。此外反复、长期使用染发剂有可能出现接触性皮炎，长期使用（密集使用三年以上）甚至可能增加患白血病的风险。</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"pre\" style=\"margin-top:7.5pt;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;\">提醒广大消费者前往不要像我一样被这种一洗黑产品蒙蔽，伤了身边的亲人，害了自己的秀发！</span></span><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"pre\" style=\"margin-top:7.5pt;margin-bottom:7.5pt;text-indent:24pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:12pt;background-image:initial;background-attachment:initial;background-size:initial;background-origin:initial;background-clip:initial;background-position:initial;background-repeat:initial;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><img src=\"../../upload/20170410134325_64132.jpg\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>','','','2017-04-10 01:44:38','','0','0','1');
